var book = {
	"name": "1 Syiem",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u syiem Dabid u la tymmen bad u la noh arsut ka rta; bad haba ki pyntap ïa u da ki jaiñ ruh, um syaid shuh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar kata, ki shakri jong u ki la ong ha u, “To kin ïawad ïa u syiem kynrad kawei ka samla basotti: bad to kan ïeng ha khmat u syiem, bad kan sumar ïa u; bad to ai ba kan thiah ha ka shadem jong me, ba u syiem kynrad jong nga un ïoh syaid.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, ki la ïawad kawei ka samla babhabriew ha ki phang ka ri Israel baroh, bad ki la shem ïa ka Abishag ka nong Shunam, bad ki la wallam ïa ka ha u syiem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kata ka samla te ka la bhabriew eh; bad ka la sumar ïa u syiem, bad ka la shakri ïa u; hynrei, u syiem um shym la ithuh ïa ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Adonijah u khun ka Haggith u la pynpaw khmat ïa lade, u da ong, “Ngan long syiem ma nga”: te u la pynkhreh ki kali bad ki nongshong kulai, bad sanphew ngut ki rangbah ban mareh ha shuwa jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u kpa jong u um ju pynsngewsih ïa u mynno mynno ruh ban ong, “Balei me la leh kumta?” Bad u la long ruh uba bhabriew eh; bad la kha ïa u de hadien u Absalom.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la ïasylla bad u Joab u khun ka Seruïah, bad u Abiathar lyngdoh de; te haba ki ïabud ïa u Adonijah ki la ïarap ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u Sadok lyngdoh, bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad u Shimei, bad u Rei, bad ki rangbah khraw bor jong u Dabid, kim shym la leit lem bad u Adonijah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Adonijah u la pynïap ïa ki langbrot bad ki masi bad ïa kiba sngaid hajan u maw Soheleth, uba hajan En-rogel; bad u la khot ïa ki para jong u baroh ki khun u syiem, bad ïa baroh ki rangbah Judah ki shakri u syiem:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynrei, ïa u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad u Benaïah, bad ki rangbah bakhraw, bad u Solomon u para jong u, um shym la khot.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Nathan te u la kren ha ka Bathsheba ka kmie u Solomon, u da ong, “Pham shym ïohsngew ba u Adonijah u khun ka Haggith u synshar, bad u Dabid u kynrad jong ngi um tip ïa kata?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ïa, to shah ngan pyni buit ïa pha, ba pha lah ban pynim ïa la ka jingim, bad ïa ka jingim u khun jong pha u Solomon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Khie pha, leit shapoh sha u Dabid syiem, bad ong ha u, ‘Mem shym la smai ha ka shakri jong me, syiem kynrad, me da ong, “Da shisha u Solomon u khun jong pha un synshar ynda khyllait ma nga, bad un shong halor ka khet jong nga?” balei te ba u Adonijah u synshar?’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha khmih, katba pha dang kren hangta bad u syiem, nga ruh ngan wan rung hadien jong pha, bad ngan pynskhem ïa ka ktien jong pha.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, ka Bathsheba ka la leit rung sha u syiem shapoh ka kamra: bad u syiem u la tymmen eh; ka Abishag ka nong Shunam te ka la shakri ïa u syiem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka Bathsheba ka la dem ngon, bad ka la nguh ïa u syiem. Te u syiem u la ong, “Pha kwah aïu?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka te ka la ong ïa u, “Kynrad, me la smai da U Trai U Blei jong me ha la ka shakri, me da ong, ‘Da shisha u Solomon u khun jong pha un synshar ynda khyllait ma nga, bad un shong halor ka khet jong nga.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te mynta, ha khmih, u Adonijah u synshar; bad me, ko syiem kynrad, mem tip ïa kata:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u la pynïap ïa ki masi bad kiba sngaid bad ïa ki langbrot byllai, bad u la khot ïa ki khun u syiem baroh, bad ïa u Abiathar lyngdoh, bad ïa u Joab u kaptan ki paidïapom: hynrei, ïa u Solomon u shakri jong me um shym ïakhot.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ma me, ko syiem kynrad, ki khmat ki Israel baroh ki ha me, ba men ïathuh ha ki uno un shong halor ka khet u syiem kynrad jong nga hadien jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, kan jia, ynda u syiem kynrad jong nga un thiah bad ki kpa jong u, ba ïa nga bad ïa u Solomon u khun jong nga yn ñiew ki bapop.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te, ha khmih, katba ka dang ïakren bad u syiem, u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa u la wan rung.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki la ïathuh te ha u syiem, ki ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, utai u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa.” Te haba u la rung ha khmat u syiem, u la dem ngon la ka khmat sha khyndew ha khmat u syiem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Nathan te u la ong, “A syiem kynrad, me la ong, ‘U Adonijah un synshar hadien jong nga, bad shong halor ka khet jong nga?’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Namar u la leit hiar ha kane ka sngi, bad u la pynïap ki masi bad kiba sngaid bad ki langbrot byllai, bad u la khot ïa ki khun u syiem baroh, bad ïa ki kaptan ki paidïapom, bad ïa u Abiathar lyngdoh; te ha khmih, ki ïabam ki ïadih ha khmat jong u, bad ki ïa-ong, ‘To U Blei un pynim ïa u syiem Adonijah.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ïa nga, nga keiñ u shakri jong me, bad u Sadok lyngdoh, bad ïa u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad ïa u Solomon u shakri jong me, um shym ïakhot.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ïa kane u la leh u syiem kynrad jong nga, bad mem shym la pyni ha la ki shakri uno u ban shong ha ka khet u syiem kynrad jong nga hadien jong u?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Dabid u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Khot ha nga ïa ka Bathsheba.” Ka te ka la wan ha khmat u syiem, bad ka la ïeng ha khmat u syiem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U syiem te u la smai bad u la ong, “Katba im U Trai, uba la pyllait ïa ka mynsiem jong nga na ka jingjynjar baroh,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> shisha kumba nga la smai ha pha da U Trai U Blei ki Israel, nga da ong, ‘Da shisha u Solomon u khun jong pha un synshar ynda khyllait ma nga, bad un shong halor ka khet jong nga ha ka jaka jong nga’; kumta da shisha ngan leh ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Bathsheba ka la nguh la ka khmat sha khyndew, bad ka la nguh ïa u syiem, ka la ong ruh, “To u syiem kynrad jong nga u Dabid un im junom.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u syiem Dabid u la ong, “Khot ha nga ïa u Sadok lyngdoh, bad ïa u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad ïa u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada.” Kumta, ki la wan ha khmat u syiem.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha ki, “Ïalam bad phi ïa ki shakri u kynrad jong phi, bad to pynshong ïa u Solomon u khun jong nga halor u kadda jong nga hi, bad leit lam ïa u shathie sha Gihon:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad to u Sadok lyngdoh bad u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa kin pynsleh ïa u hangta ban long u syiem halor ki Israel: bad to put phi da ka turoi, bad to ong, ‘U Blei un pynim ïa u Solomon syiem.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ynda kumta, phin wan kiew nadien jong u, bad un wan shong halor ka khet jong nga; naba u un long u syiem ha ka jaka jong nga: bad nga la thung ïa u ban long u nongïalam halor ki Israel bad halor ki Judah.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada u la ïathuh ha u syiem, u da ong, “Amen: U Trai, U Blei jong u kynrad jong nga u syiem, un ong kumta.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kumba U Trai u la long lem bad u kynrad jong nga u syiem, kumta keiñ un long bad u Solomon, bad un pynlong kham khraw ïa ka khet jong u ban ïa ka khet u Dabid u syiem kynrad jong nga.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kumta, u Sadok lyngdoh bad u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad ki Khereth bad ki Peleth, ki la leit hiar, bad ki la pynshong ïa u Solomon halor u kadda u syiem Dabid, bad ki la leit lam ïa u sha Gihon.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Sadok lyngdoh u la shim ka reng umphniang na Ka Tabernakl, bad u la pynsleh ïa u Solomon. Bad ki la put ïa ka turoi; bad u paidbah baroh u la ong, “U Blei un pynim ïa u Solomon syiem.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te u paidbah baroh u la wan bud artet ïa u, bad u paidbah u la put ki sharati, bad ki la ïakmen da ka jingkmen bakhraw, kat ban pdang ka khyndew da ka jingrisa jong ki.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Adonijah bad kita ki lok kiba bad u baroh ki la ïohsngew katba ki dang lah ïabam. Te haba u Joab u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa, u la ong, “Balei ba jam kumne ka shnong bakhynwin?”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Katba u dang kren, ha khmih, u Jonathan u khun u Abiathar u lyngdoh u la wan: bad u Adonijah u la ong, “To wan rung; naba me long u briew u babha bad me wallam ki khubor babha.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ïathuh, bad u la ong ha u Adonijah, “Shisha u Dabid u syiem kynrad jong ngi u la pynlong syiem ïa u Solomon:",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad u syiem u la phah lem bad u ïa u Sadok lyngdoh, bad ïa u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, bad ïa ki Khereth bad ki Peleth bad ki la pynshong ïa u halor u kadda u syiem:",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> bad u Sadok lyngdoh bad u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa ki la pynsleh syiem ïa u ha Gihon: bad ki ïawan artet noh nangta da kaba ïalehkmen, ba kumta ka shnong ka la khynwin pat. Kane keiñ ka jingsawa ba phi la ïohsngew.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad u Solomon u shong ruh halor ka khet jong ka hima.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad nalor kata ki shakri u syiem ki la ïawan ban kyrkhu ïa u syiem Dabid u kynrad jong ngi, ki ïa-ong, ‘U Blei jong me un pynlong ïa ka kyrteng u Solomon kham khraw ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad un pynlong ïa ka khet jong u kham khraw ïa ka khet jong me’: te u syiem u la dem ha la ka jingthiah.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te kumne ruh u la ong u syiem, ‘Long ba la kyrkhu U Trai, U Blei jong ki Israel, uba la ai ïa u ban shong halor ka khet jong nga ha kane ka sngi, katba ki khmat jong nga ki dang ïohi.’ ”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te kita baroh ki lok u Adonijah ki la sheptieng, bad haba ki la ïeng joit, ki la leit uwei uwei baroh sha la kaba leit.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te u Adonijah u la kyiuh na ka bynta u Solomon; bad haba u la khie joit, u la leit bat na ki reng jong ka duwan.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ïa u Solomon, ki da ong, “Ha khmih, u Adonijah u sheptieng ïa u Solomon syiem: naba, ha khmih, u la bat na ki reng ka duwan, u da ong, ‘To u syiem Solomon un smai ha nga ha kane ka sngi ba un ym pynïap ïa u shakri jong u da ka waitlam.’ ”",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U Solomon te u la ong, “Lada un pyni ïa lade u briew uba dei, iwei i shñiuh jong u in ym hap ha khyndew: hynrei, lada shem ka jingbymman ha u, un ïap keiñ.”",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Kumta, u syiem Solomon u la phah, bad ki la wallam noh ïa u na kata ka duwan. Te u la wan bad u la nguh ïa u Solomon: te u Solomon u la ong ha u, “Khie leit sha la ïing.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki sngi u Dabid ki la jan ba un ïap; bad u la hukum ïa u Solomon u khun jong u, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Nga leit sha ka lynti ka pyrthei baroh: me namar kata, to long uba khlaiñ, bad to leh rangbah ïa lade;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad to sumar ïa ka kam U Trai U Blei jong me, ïa ka ban ïaid ha ki lynti jong u, ban sumar ïa ki aiñ jong u, bad ki hukum jong u, bad ïa ki jingbishar jong u, bad ïa ki jingphla jong u, kat kumba la thoh ha ka hukum u Moses, ba men man roi ha kaba me leh baroh, bad kat shaba men phai:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ba U Trai un pynskhem ïa ka ktien jong u kaba u la kren shaphang jong nga, u da ong, ‘Lada ki khun jong me kin sumar ha ka lynti jong ki, ban ïaid ha khmat jong nga ha ka jingshisha da ka dohnud jong ki baroh bad ka mynsiem jong ki baroh, yn ym duh ïa me (u la ong) u briew halor ka khet Israel.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Nalor kata ruh, me tip ïa kaei ba u Joab u khun ka Seruïah u la leh ïa nga, kaei ba u la leh keiñ ïa ki ar ngut ki rangbah ki paidïapom ki Israel, ïa u Abner u khun u Ner, bad ïa u Amasa u khun u Jether, kiba u la pynïap, bad u la pynmih ïa ka snam ka thma ha kaba suk, bad u la tah ka snam ka thma ha la ka jingpanpoh kaba ha ka syngkai jong u, bad ha la ki juti kiba ha ki sla'jat jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> To leh namar kata katba kum ka jingstad jong me, bad wat shah ïa ka khlieh 'ñiuhlieh jong u ban leit sha ka jingtep ha ka jingsuk.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, to leh sbun ha ki khun u Barsillai u nong Gilead, bad to ai ba kin long na kita ki ban bam ha ka miej jong me: naba kumta ki la ïawan sha nga mynba nga la phet na u Absalom u hynmen jong me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te, ha khmih, don bad me u Shimei u khun u Gera, u nong Benjamin, na Bahurim, uba la tim ïa nga da ka jingtim kaba jur ha kata ka sngi mynba nga la leit sha Mahanaim: hynrei, u la wan hiar ban tan ïa nga ha Jordan, bad nga la smai ha u da U Trai, nga la ong, ‘Ngan ym pynïap ïa me da ka waitlam.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te mynta wat kheiñ ïa u uba khlem pop, naba me long u briew bastad; bad me tip kaei me dei ban leh ïa u, bad men pynhiar ïa ka khlieh 'ñiuhlieh jong u bad ka snam sha ka jingtep.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta u Dabid u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki sngi ba u Dabid u la synshar halor ki Israel ki la long sawphew snem: hynñiew snem u la synshar ha Hebron bad laiphew lai snem u la synshar ha Jerusalem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Solomon u la shong halor ka khet u Dabid u kpa jong u; bad ïa ka hima jong u la pynskhem shikatdei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Adonijah u khun ka Haggith u la wan sha ka Bathsheba ka kmie u Solomon. Ka te ka la ong, “Me wan da kaba suk?” Bad u la ong, “Da kaba suk keiñ.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U la ong te, “Nga don ei ei ban ong ha pha.” Ka te ka la ong, “To ong.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong te, “Pha tip ba ka hima ka la long ka jong nga, bad ba ki Israel baroh ki la peit la ki khmat ha nga, ba ngan synshar, pynban, ka hima ka la phai da kumwei, bad ka la long ka jong u para jong nga: naba ka la long ka jong u na U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te mynta nga pan ïa kawei ka jingpan na pha, wat kyrngah ïa nga.” Ka la ong te ha u, “To ong.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U te u la ong, “To kren, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ha u Solomon syiem (naba un ym ong em ïa pha,) ba un ai ïa ka Abishag ka nong Shunam ban long ka tnga jong nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka Bathsheba ka la ong te, “Ñiuma; ngan kren na ka bynta jong me ha u syiem.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka Bathsheba namar kata ka la leit sha u Solomon syiem, ban kren ha u na ka bynta u Adonijah. Te u syiem u la ïeng joit ban shaw ïa ka, bad u la nguh ïa ka, bad u la shong halor la ka khet, bad u la phah buh ka khet ïa ka kmie u syiem; bad ka la shong sha ka kti kamon jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la ong, “Nga pan ïa kawei ka jingpan kaba rit na me; wat ong em ïa nga.” U syiem te u la ong ïa ka, “To pan, ko mei: naba ngan ym ong em ïa pha.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “To ai ïa ka Abishag ka nong Shunam ha u Adonijah u hynmen jong me ban long ka tnga jong u.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Solomon syiem u la ïathuh te bad u la ong ïa la ka kmie, “Balei ba pha pan ïa ka Abishag ka nong Shunam ïa u Adonijah? to pan ïa u ïa ka hima ruh; naba u long u hynmen jong nga; ïa u keiñ, bad ïa u Abiathar lyngdoh, bad ïa u Joab u khun ka Seruïah.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon syiem u la smai da U Trai, u da ong, “U Blei un leh kumta ïa nga, bad kham tam ruh, lada u Adonijah um shym la kren ïa kane ka ktien pyrshah ïa la ka jong ka jingim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar kata te, katba im U Trai, uba la thung ïa nga, bad uba la buh ïa nga halor ka khet u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad u la pynlong ïing ïa nga, kumba u la kular, shisha yn pynïap ïa u Adonijah ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Solomon syiem u la phah da ka kti u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada; bad u la ktah kti ïa u, ba u la ïap.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U syiem te u la ong ïa u Abiathar lyngdoh, “Khie me sha Anathoth, sha la ki khyndew; naba me long u briew uba dei ban ïap: hynrei, ngan ym pynïap ïa me ha kane ka por, namar me la bah ïa ka synduk U Trai U Blei ha khmat u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad namar ba la pynshitom ïa me ha baroh ha kaba la pynshitom ïa u kpa jong nga.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la beh noh ïa u Abiathar na kaba long lyngdoh ha U Trai; ba un pyndep ïa ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren shaphang ka ïing u Eli ha Sheiloh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te la poi khubor ha u Joab: naba u Joab u la bud ïa u Adonijah, la um shym la bud ïa u Absalom. Te u Joab u la phet sha Ka Tabernakl U Trai, bad u la bat na ki reng ka duwan.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> La ïathuh te ïa u Solomon syiem, ba u Joab u la phet sha Ka Tabernakl U Trai, bad, ha khmih, u don hajan kata ka duwan. Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la phah ïa u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada, u da ong, “To leit, to ktah kti ïa u.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Benaïah u la wan sha Ka Tabernakl U Trai, bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong u syiem, ‘To mih noh.’ ” U te u la ong, “Em; hynrei ngan ïap hangne.” Bad u Benaïah u la wallam ktien pat ha u syiem, u da ong, “Kumta u la ong u Joab, bad kumta u la phai ktien ïa nga.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U syiem te u la ong ïa u, “Leh kumba u la ong, bad to ktah kti ïa u, bad tep noh ïa u; ba men sait noh na nga bad na ka ïing u kpa jong nga ïa kata ka snam, kaba u Joab u la pynmih khlem daw.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te U Trai un pynphai ïa ka snam jong u halor ka khlieh jong u hi, namar u la ktah kti ïa ki ar ngut ki rangbah kiba kham hok bad kham bha ban ïa u, bad u la pynïap ïa ki da ka waitlam, te u Dabid u kpa jong nga um shym da tip ïa kata, kita, u Abner u khun u Ner, u kaptan ki paidïapom ki Israel, bad u Amasa u khun u Jether, u kaptan ki paidïapom ki Judah.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta, ka snam jong ki kan phai halor ka khlieh u Joab, bad halor ka khlieh u symbai jong u ha la ka rta: hynrei, ha u Dabid, bad ha u symbai jong u, bad ha ka ïing jong u, bad ha ka khet jong u, kan long ka jingsuk ha la ka rta na U Trai.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kumta, u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada u la leit kiew, bad u la ktah kti ïa u, bad u la pynïap ïa u; bad la tep ïa u ha la ïing hi ha ri khlaw.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u syiem u la buh ïa u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada ha ka jaka jong u halor u paidïapom: bad ïa u Sadok lyngdoh, u syiem u la buh ha ka jaka u Abiathar.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u syiem u la phah khot ïa u Shimei, bad u la ong ïa u, “To tei ïing ïa me ha Jerusalem, bad shong khop hangta, bad wat mih noh nangta shano shano ruh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Naba ha kata ka sngi ba men mih noh, bad jam palat ïa ita i wah Kidron, to tip skhem ba men ïap shisha: ka snam jong me kan long halor ka khlieh jong me hi.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U Shimei te u la ong ha u syiem, “Kata ka jingong ka babha: kumba u syiem kynrad u la ong, kumta u shakri jong me un leh.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Shimei u la shong ha Jerusalem bun sngi. Te ynda la lai snem, ar ngut na ki shakri jong u Shimei ki la phet noh ha u Akhish, u khun u Maakah, u syiem ka Gath. Ki la ïathuh te ha u Shimei, ki da ong, “Ha khmih, ki shakri jong me ki ha Gath.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te haba u Shimei u la ïeng, bad u la teh jin ïa la ka kadda, u la leit sha Gath sha u Akhish, ban wad ïa la ki shakri: bad u Shimei u la leit, bad u la wallam noh ïa la ki shakri na Gath.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Solomon ba u Shimei u la leit na Jerusalem sha Gath, bad ba u la wan phai pat.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U syiem te u la phah khot ïa u Shimei, bad u la ong ha u, “Nga ngam la pynsmai ïa me da U Trai, bad nga la ong skhem ha me, nga da ong, ‘To tip skhem, ba ha kata ka sngi ba men mih noh, bad men ïaid shabar shano shano ruh, men ïap shisha?’ bad me la ong ïa nga, ‘Kata ka jingong ba nga la ïohsngew ka long ka babha.’",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Balei te ba mem shym la sumar ïa ka jingsmai U Trai, bad ïa ka hukum ïa kaba nga la buh halor jong me?”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> U syiem u la ong ruh ha u Shimei, “Me tip ïa ka jingsniew baroh kaba ka dohnud jong me ka rieh, kaba me la leh ïa u Dabid u kpa jong nga: namar kata, U Trai un pynphai ïa ka jingsniew jong me halor ka khlieh jong me hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hynrei, u Solomon syiem un long uba la kyrkhu, bad ka khet u Dabid ka long kaba la pynskhem ha khmat U Trai, ha la ka rta.”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kumta, u syiem u la hukum ïa u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada; te haba u la mih noh, u la ktah kti ïa u, bad u la ïap. Te ïa ka hima la pynskhem ha ka kti u Solomon."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Solomon u la pynlong ka jingïashongkha bad u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt, bad u la shim ïa ka khun u Pharaoh, bad u la wallam ïa ka sha ka shnong u Dabid, tad ynda u la lah pyndep kaba tei ïa ka ïing la ka jong, bad ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ka kynroh ka Jerusalem baroh sawdong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U paidbah te u la ju kñia ha kita ki jaka bajrong, namar ba haduh kita ki sngi ym pat tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Solomon u la ieit ïa U Trai, u da ïaid ha ki aiñ u Dabid u kpa jong u: hynrei, u la kñia bad u la thang ka jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u syiem u la leit sha Gibeon ban kñia hangta; naba kata ka la long ka jaka bajrong kaba khraw keiñ: shi hajar ki jingainguh thang u Solomon u la kñia halor kata ka duwan.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ha Gibeon U Trai u la paw ha u Solomon ha ka jingphohsniew mynmiet: bad U Blei u la ong, “To pan kaei ngan ai ha me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Solomon te u la ong, “Me la pyni ka jingsbun bakhraw ha u shakri jong me u Dabid u kpa jong nga, kat kumba u la ïaid ha khmat jong me ha ka jingshisha, bad ha ka hok, bad ha ka jingbeit ka dohnud bad me; bad me la tyngkai na ka bynta jong u ïa kane ka jingsbun bakhraw, ba me la ai ha u, u khun ban shong halor ka khet jong u, kumba ka long ha kane ka sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mynta te, A Trai U Blei jong nga, me la pynlong syiem ïa la u shakri ha ka jaka u Dabid u kpa jong nga: bad nga long tang u khynnah u barit; ngam tip kumno ban mih shabar lane ban rung shapoh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u shakri jong me u long hapdeng u paidbah jong me uba me la jied, u paidbah bakhraw, u bym lah ban ñiew lymne kheiñ namar babun eh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To ai ha la u shakri, namar kata, ka dohnud ba sngewthuh ban bishar ïa u paidbah jong me, ba nga lah ban ithuh ïa ka babha bad ka basniew; naba uei uba lah ban bishar kat une u paidbah u bakhraw jong me?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kata ka jingkren te ka la pynsngewbha ïa U Trai, ba u Solomon u la pan ïa kum kane.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Blei u la ong ïa u, “Namar ba me la pan ïa kane, bad ba mem shym la pan ïa lade ban im slem; lymne mem shym la pan ka spah ïa lade, lymne mem shym la pan ïa ka jingim ki nongshun jong me; hynrei, me la pan ïa lade ka jingshemphang ban sngewthuh ïa ka jingbishar;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ha khmih, nga la leh katba kum ka ktien jong me: ha khmih, nga la ai ha me ka dohnud bastad bad bashemphang; kumta, ba ym shym la don uwei uba kum me mynshuwa jong me, lymne hadien jong me un ym mih uba kum me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te nga la ai ruh ha me kata kaba mem shym la pan, ka spah bad ka burom ruh, kumta, ban ym don uwei hapdeng ki syiem uba kum me, ha ki sngi jong me baroh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad lada men ïaid ha ka lynti jong nga, ban sumar ïa ki aiñ bad ki hukum jong nga, kumba u Dabid u kpa jong me u la ïaid, te ngan pynjlan ïa ki sngi jong me.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Solomon u la kyndit, bad, ha khmih, ka la long ka jingphohsniew: bad haba u la wan sha Jerusalem, u la ïeng ha khmat ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, bad u la kñia ki jingainguh thang, bad u la kñia ki jingainguh pynïasuk, bad u la pynlong ka jingkhawai ha la ki shakri baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la wan ar ngut ki kynthei, kiba long ki nuti, ha u syiem, bad ki la ïeng ha khmat jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kawei ka kynthei ka la ong, “A kynrad jong nga, ma nga bad kane ka kynthei ngi ïashong ha kawei ka ïing; bad nga la kha i khun lem bad ka ha kata ka ïing.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ka la jia ha ka sngi ka balai hadien ba nga la kha, ba kane ka briew ruh ka la kha; te ngi ïadon lang, ym don nongwei lem bad ngi ha kata ka ïing, tang ngi ar ngut ha ïing.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te i khun kane ka briew i la ïap mynmiet; namar ka la kum ban ïa i.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad haba ka la khie shiteng synñia, ka la shim ïa i khun jong nga na ka krung jong nga, haba dang thiah ka shakri jong me, bad ka la pynthiah ïa i ha ka shadem jong ka, bad ka la pynthiah ïa i khun ïap jong ka ha ka shadem jong nga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba nga la khie mynstep ban ai buiñ ïa la i khun, ha khmih, i la ïap: hynrei, ynda nga la lah khmih thuh ïa i mynstep, ha khmih, im dei i khun jong nga, iba nga la kha.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kata kawei ka briew te ka la ong, “Em; hynrei, u ba-im u khun jong nga, bad u baïap u khun jong pha.” Kane te ka la ong, “Em; hynrei, u baïap u khun jong pha, bad u ba-im u khun jong nga.” Kumta ki la ïakren ha khmat u syiem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ong, “Kawei ka ong, ‘Une u ba-im u khun jong nga, bad u baïap u khun jong pha:’ bad katai kawei ka ong, ‘Em; hynrei u baïap u khun jong pha, bad u ba-im u khun jong nga.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u syiem u la ong, “Am ka talwar ha nga.” Bad ki la wallam ha khmat u syiem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U syiem u la ong te, “To phiah ar liang ïa une u khun im, bad ai shiteng ha kawei, bad shiteng ha kawei pat.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la kren ha u syiem kata ka briew kaba ita i khun i ba-im i dei i jong ka, naba ka dohnud jong ka, ka la thnam na ka bynta i khun jong ka, bad ka la ong, “A kynrad, to ai ha ka ïa i khun im, bad da lei lei wat pynïap ïa i.” Hynrei, kata kawei ka la ong, “Wat ai in long i jong nga lymne i jong pha; phiah ïa i.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U syiem te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “To ai ha kata ïa i khun im, bad da lei lei wat pynïap ïa i: ka dei ma ka, ka kmie jong i.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki Israel baroh ki la ïohsngew ïa kata ka jingbishar ïa kaba u syiem u la bishar; bad ki la sheptieng ïa u syiem: naba ki la ïohi ba ka jingstad U Blei ka la don ha u, ban leh ïa ka jingbishar."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta u Solomon syiem u la long u syiem halor ki Israel baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kine ki la long ki rangbah syiem kiba u la don: u Asariah u khun u Sadok lyngdoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Elihoreph bad u Ahijah, ki khun u Shisha, ki nongthoh; u Jehoshaphat u khun u Ahilud, u nongthoh bui.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Benaïah u khun u Jehoïada u la long halor u paidïapom; u Sadok ruh bad u Abiathar ki la long lyngdoh;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Asariah u khun u Nathan u la long halor ki rangbah; bad u Sabud u khun u Nathan u la long u shakri rangbah, bad u lok jong u syiem;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Ahishar u la long halor ka ïing; bad u Adoniram u khun u Abda u la long halor ka khrong.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Solomon u la don khat-ar ngut ki rangbah halor ki Israel baroh, kiba la taïar jingbam ïa u syiem bad ïa ka ïing jong u: uwei uwei u briew u dei ban taïar jingbam shi bnai ha ka shi snem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kine ki kyrteng jong ki: u Ben-hur, ha ri lum Ephraim:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> u Ben-deker, ha Makas, bad ha Shaalbim, bad Beth-shemesh, bad Elon-beth-hanan:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u Ben-hesed, ha Arubboth; ha u ka dei ka Sokoh, bad ka ri Hepher baroh:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u Ben-abinadab, ha Naphath-Dor baroh; u la shongkurim bad ka Taphath ka khun u Solomon:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u Baana u khun u Ahilud, ha Taanakh bad Megiddo, bad ka Beth-shean baroh kaba hajan ka Sarethan harum ka Jesril, naduh Beth-shean haduh Abel-meholah, jin haduh palat ka Jokmeam:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u Ben-geber, ha Ramoth-gilead; ha u ka dei ki shnong u Jair u khun u Manasseh, kiba ha Gilead: ha u ka dei ka ri Argob, kaba ha Bashan, hynñiewphew ki nongbah kiba khraw kiba ker kynroh bad ki dieng khang rnong:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u Ahinadab u khun u Iddo, ha Mahanaim:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Ahimaas, ha Naphtali; u ruh u la shongkurim bad ka Bashemath ka khun u Solomon:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> u Baana u khun u Hushai, ha Asher bad ha Bealoth;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> u Jehoshaphat u khun u Paruah, na Issakhar;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> u Shimei u khun u Ela, ha Benjamin:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> u Geber u khun u Uri, ha ka ri Gilead, ka ri u Sihon u syiem ki Amor bad ka jong u Og u syiem ka Bashan; te tang ma u, u rangbah uba ha kata ka ri.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki Judah bad ki Israel ki bun kat u shyiap harud duriaw ha ka jingbun, ki ïabam ki ïadih bad ki ïalehkmen.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Solomon u la synshar halor ki hima baroh naduh kata ka Wah haduh ka ri ki Philistia, bad haduh ka pud ka ri Ijipt: ki la wallam ki jingnguh syiem, bad ki la shakri ïa u Solomon ha ki sngi ka rta jong u baroh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka jingbam jong u Solomon te shi sngi shi sngi la long laiphew byrni u moida bani, bad hynriewphew byrni u 'purew:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> shiphew tylli ki masi ba la pynsngaid, bad arphew ki masi bam phlang, bad shispah ki langbrot, nalor ki bthong, ki khiat, bad ki 'keirang, bad ki syiar ba la pynsngaid.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar u la synshar halor ka ri baroh shaphang shane kata ka Wah, naduh Tiphsah haduh Gasa, halor ki syiem baroh shaphang shane jong kata ka Wah. Bad u la suk ha ki phang baroh sawdong jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki Judah bad ki Israel ki la shong ha kaba suk, uwei pa uwei hapoh la u jong u dieng Waiñ bad la u jong u dieng Dumbur, naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba, baroh ki sngi jong u Solomon.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Solomon u la don sawphew hajar ki sem kulai ïa ki kali jong u, bad khat-ar hajar ngut ki nongshong kulai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad kita ki rangbah ki ju taïar jingbam ïa u Solomon syiem, bad ïa kita baroh kiba ju wan ha ka miej u Solomon, uwei uwei u briew ha la u bnai: kim duna ei ei.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Kew Barli ruh bad u skum ïa ki kulai bad ïa ki dromedari ki ju wallam ha ka jaka ba kita ki rangbah ki la ïadon, u briew baroh katba shong ka kam jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad U Blei u la ai ïa u Solomon ka jingstad bad ka jingshemphang shikatdei eh, bad ka jingkhraw ka dohnud, kum u shyiap uba harud duriaw.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka jingstad u Solomon ka la palat ïa ka jingstad ki khun ka ri mihngi baroh, bad ïa ka jingstad ka ri Ijipt baroh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Naba u la long kham stad ban ïa ki briew baroh; ban ïa u Ethan u nong Esrah, bad ïa u Heman, bad u Kalkol, bad u Darda, ki khun u Mahol: bad ka nam jong u ka la don ha baroh ki jaid bynriew kiba kylleng sawdong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u la kren lai hajar ki proberb: bad ki jingrwai jong u ki la long shi hajar bad san.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la kren shaphang ki dieng, naduh u Kedar uba ha Lebanon haduh u Hyssop uba mih na ka kynroh: u la kren shaphang ki mrad ruh, bad shaphang ki sim, bad shaphang ki kynja bapar, bad shaphang ki dohkha de.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ki kynja bynriew baroh ki la wan ban sngew ïa ka jingstad u Solomon, na ki syiem ka pyrthei baroh kiba la ïohsngew shaphang ka jingstad jong u."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Hiram u syiem ka Tyros u la phah ïa la ki shakri ha u Solomon; namar u la lah ïohsngew ba ki la lah thung syiem ïa u ha ka jaka u kpa jong u: naba u Hiram u la ju long uba ieit ïa u Dabid.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Solomon te u la phah sha u Hiram, u da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Me tip kumno ba u Dabid u kpa jong nga um lah ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei jong u, namar kita ki thma kiba baroh sawdong ïa u, tad ynda U Trai u la buh ïa ki hapoh ki sla'jat jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei mynta, U Trai U Blei jong nga u la ai ha nga kaba suk suda baroh sawdong; ym don u nongïaleh pyrshah, lymne ka jingjia basniew.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha khmih, nga thmu ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei jong nga, kumba U Trai u la kren ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, u da ong, ‘U khun jong me, uba ngan pynshong halor ka khet jong me ha ka jaka jong me, un tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga.’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar kata te, to hukum ma me ba kin khet ki dieng Kedar ïa nga na Lebanon; bad ki shakri jong nga kin long bad ki shakri jong me; te ngan ai ha me ka bainong na ka bynta ki shakri jong me katba kum baroh ba men ong: namar me tip bymdon hapdeng jong ngi uno uno uba nang ban khet dieng kum ki nong Sidon.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda u Hiram u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien u Solomon, u la kmen eh, bad u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai ha kane ka sngi, uba la ai ha u Dabid u khun u bastad halor une u paidbah bakhraw.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Hiram u la phah ktien ha u Solomon, u da ong, “Nga la ïohsngew ki ktien kiba me la phah ha nga: ngan pyndep ïa ka jingkwah jong me baroh shaphang ki dieng Kedar, bad shaphang ki dieng Kseh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki shakri jong nga kin pynhiar noh ïa ki na Lebanon sha ka duriaw: bad ngan teh bur ïa ki ban leit na duriaw sha ka jaka ba men buh ïa nga, bad ngan law noh ïa ki hangta, bad men shim noh ïa ki: hynrei, men pynbiang ïa ka jingkwah jong nga, da kaba ai jingbam ïa ka ïing jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u Hiram u la ai ïa u Solomon ïa ki dieng Kedar bad ki dieng Kseh ïa ka jingkwah jong u baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Solomon u la ai ïa u Hiram arphew hajar byrni u Kew ban bam ha ka ïing jong u, bad arphew hajar ki khra umphniang babha: kumne u Solomon u ju ai ïa u Hiram man la ka snem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Trai u la ai ka jingstad ïa u Solomon, kumba u la kular ïa u; bad la don ka jingïasuk hapdeng u Hiram bad u Solomon; bad ki la ïa-pynlong ka jingïateh lok baroh ar ngut.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la pynmih ki khar paid na ki Israel baroh; kita ki khar paid te ki la long laiphew hajar ki briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la phah ïa ki sha Lebanon, shiphew hajar shi bnai shi bnai kylliang kylliang: shi bnai ki don ha Lebanon, bad ar bnai ha shnong: bad u Adoniram u la long halor kita ki khar paid.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Solomon u la don hynñiewphew hajar kiba kit jingkit, bad phraphew hajar kiba shtah ha ki lum;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> nalor ki sordar rangbah jong u Solomon kiba la long halor kata ka kam, lai hajar bad laispah, kiba synshar halor kita ki briew kiba trei ha kata ka kam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem u la hukum, bad ki la thlieh ïa ki maw baheh, ki maw bakordor, ïa ka ban pynshong nongrim ïa kata ka ïing da ki maw ba la shniah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki nongtrei kynroh u Solomon bad ki nongtrei kynroh u Hiram bad ki Gebal ki la ïashna ïa ki, bad ki la ïakhreh ïa ki dieng bad ki maw ïa ka ban tei ïa ka ïing."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka snem kaba sawspah phraphew, hadien ba ki khun Israel ki la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt, ha ka snem ka basaw ka jingsynshar u Solomon halor ki Israel, ha u 'nai Sib, uba long u bnai u ba-ar, u la sdang ban tei ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te kata ka ïing ïa kaba u syiem Solomon u la tei ïa U Trai, ka lynter jong ka, ka la long hynriewphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, arphew, bad ka jingjrong jong ka, laiphew pruh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka batsha ha khmat ka orakl jong ka ïing, ka lynter jong ka, ka la long arphew pruh, kat ka pyngkiang jong ka ïing; bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, ka la long shiphew pruh ha khmat ka ïing.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ïa ka ïing u la thaw ki jingkhang ïit kum kaba thain kriah pashing kiba pynskhem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha syndah ka kynroh ka ïing u la tei mala baroh sawdong, ha syndah ki kynroh ka ïing baroh sawdong, ïa ka templ bad ïa ka orakl de: bad u la thaw ki kamra baroh sawdong ka shakiar ïing:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ka mala kaba shapoh ka don san pruh pyngkiang, bad ka mala pdeng ka don hynriew pruh pyngkiang bad ka balai ka don hynñiew pruh pyngkiang: namar ha kaba shabar u la thaw ki kyrdan ha ki kynroh jong ka ïing baroh sawdong, ba ki dieng siang lyntang kin ym leit rung shapoh ki kynroh ka ïing.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ïa ka ïing te haba dang tei ïa ka, la tei da ki maw ba la shniah lypa ha ka par maw: bad ym shym la don jingsawa tyrnem lymne sdie lymne kano kano ka atiar bakynja nar ha kata ka ïing, haba dang tei ïa ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka jingkhang ïa ki kamra shakiar kiba hapdeng ka la long ha ka krung kamon jong ka ïing: bad kin kiew artet da ki kyrdan bakyllaiñ sha ki mala kiba hapdeng, bad na kaba hapdeng sha ka balai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u la tei ïa ka ïing, bad u la pyndep ïa ka, bad u la sop ïa ka ïing da ki bim bad da ki lyntang dieng Kedar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la tei kita ki mala ha syndah ka ïing baroh sawdong, kawei kawei san pruh ka jingjrong: bad la pynneh ïa ki ha ka ïing da ki dieng Kedar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Solomon, ka da ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Shaphang kane ka ïing kaba me dang tei, lada men ïaid ha ki aiñ jong nga, bad leh ïa ki jingbishar jong nga, bad sumar ïa ki hukum jong nga baroh ban ïaid ha ki; te ngan pynskhem ïa ka ktien jong nga bad me, kaba nga la kren ha u Dabid u kpa jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ngan shong hapdeng ki khun Israel, bad ngan ym iehnoh ïa u paidbah jong nga ki khun Israel.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la tei ïa kata ka ïing, bad u la pyndep ïa ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la tap ïa ki kynroh ka ïing shapoh da ki lyntang dieng Kedar; naduh tbian ka ïing haduh ka kynroh ka sad, u la tap ïa ki ha kaba shapoh da ka dieng: bad u la siang ïa ka ïing da ki lyntang Kseh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ker arphew pruh shaphang shadien ka ïing da ki lyntang dieng Kedar naduh tbian haduh bakut ki kynroh: u la ker shi bynta na kaba shapoh ban long ka orakl, ban long ka jaka kyntang tam keiñ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kata ka ïing, kaba long ka templ ha khmat jong ka, ka la long sawphew pruh ka lynter.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> La don ruh ki dieng Kedar ha ka ïing shapoh, ba la ot shrong bad ki syntiew ba la phuh: ki dieng Kedar suda; ym shym paw maw.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la khreh ïa ka orakl hapdeng ka ïing shapoh, ban buh hangta ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te shapoh kata ka orakl la don arphew pruh ka lynter, bad arphew pruh ka pyngkiang, bad arphew pruh ka jingjrong jong ka: bad u la suit ksiar ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla: bad u la sop ïa ka duwan da ki dieng Kedar.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la suit ksiar ïa ka ïing shapoh da ka ksiar banylla: bad u la tawah da ki kynjri ksiar ha khmat ka orakl; bad u la suit ïa ka da ka ksiar.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ïa ka ïing baroh kawei u la suit da ka ksiar, tad ynda la pyndep ïa kata ka ïing baroh: ïa ka duwan ruh baroh kawei kaba dei ïa ka orakl u la suit da ka ksiar.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha ka orakl te u la thaw ar tylli ki Kherub da u dieng Olib, uwei uwei shiphew pruh ka jingjrong.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kawei ka thapniang jong u Kherub ka long san pruh, bad kata kawei ka thapniang u Kherub san pruh: na bakut kawei ka thapniang sha bakut kata kawei ka la long shiphew pruh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad uwei pat u Kherub u la long shiphew pruh: baroh ar ki Kherub ki la don kawei ka jingthew bad kawei ka dur.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka jingjrong uwei u Kherub ka la long shiphew pruh, bad kumjuh ka jong uta uwei u Kherub.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kita ki Kherub hapoh ka ïing kaba kham shapoh: te kita ki Kherub ki la pyiar ïa la ki thapniang, ba kumta ka thapniang jong uwei ka kynduh ha kawei ka kynroh, bad ka thapniang jong uwei pat u Kherub ka kynduh ha kawei pat ka kynroh; bad ki thapniang jong ki, ki ïakynduh hapdeng kata ka ïing.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ïa kita ki Kherub u la suit da ka ksiar.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u la mutdur ïa ki kynroh kata ka ïing baroh sawdong da ki dur ki Kherub bad ki dieng Tlai bad ki syntiew baphuh, shapoh bad shabar.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ïa ka tbian jong ka ïing u la suit da ka ksiar, shapoh bad shabar.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ïa ka jingrung jong kata ka orakl u la thaw ki jingkhang da u dieng Olib: ka khlieh jingkhang bad ki shawkad ki la long shi bynta na kaba san bynta jong ka kynroh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta u la thaw ar tylli ki jingkhang da u dieng Olib; bad u la mutdur ha ki da ki Kherub bad ki dieng Tlai bad ki syntiew baphuh, bad u la suit ïa ki da ka ksiar; bad u la suit ïa kita ki Kherub da ka ksiar, bad ïa kita ki dieng Tlai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta ruh ïa ka jingrung ka templ u la thaw ki shawkad da u dieng Olib, na shi pawa jong ka kynroh;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad ar tylli ki jingkhang da u dieng Kseh; bad ki ar tylli ki khylliap jong kawei ka jingkhang ki la kli, bad ki ar tylli ki khylliap jong kata kawei ka jingkhang ki la kli.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u la mutdur ha ki da ki Kherub bad ki dieng Tlai bad ki syntiew baphuh: bad u la suit ksiar ïa ki da ka ksiar bapyndait ha kata ka dur ba la mut.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u la tei ïa ka phyllaw kaba kham shapoh da ki lai syrtap ki maw ba la shniah, bad shi syrtap da ki bim Kedar.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ha ka snem ka basaw la seng nongrim ïa ka ïing jong U Trai, ha u 'nai Sib.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad ha ka snem ka bakhatwei, ha u 'nai Bul, uba long u bnai u baphra, ïa ka ïing la pyndep ha ki bynta baroh jong ka, bad katba kum ka dur jong ka baroh. Kumta, u la long hynñiew snem ha kaba tei ïa ka."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Solomon u la tei ïa ka ïing la ka jong khatlai snem, bad u la pyndep ïa ka ïing jong u baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar u la tei ïa ka ïing na ka khlaw Lebanon; ka lynter jong ka, ka la long shispah pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka sanphew pruh, bad ka jingjrong jong ka laiphew pruh, halor ki rishot Kedar saw lynter, bad ki bim Kedar halor kita ki rishot.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad la tap ïa ka, da ki dieng Kedar na shalor haneng kita ki sawphew san tylli ki bim, kiba la don halor kita ki rishot; khatsan tylli shilynter.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad la don ki jingkhmih ha kine ki lai lynter, bad ka jingshai ka la don marpyrshah ka jingshai ha ki lai lynter riang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki jingkhang bad ki shawkad baroh ki long sawdong bad ki jingkhang ïit: bad ka jingshai ka marpyrshah ka jingshai ha ki lai lynter riang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka batsha da ki rishot; ka lynter jong ka, ka la long sanphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, laiphew pruh; bad ka batsha ha khmat jong ki; bad ki rishot bad ki bim barben ha khmat jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka batsha jong ka khet ha kaba un bishar, ka batsha ka jingbishar keiñ: bad la siang ïa ka da ki dieng Kedar nadong shadong.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ka ïing jong u ha kaba un shong, kata kawei pat ka ïing hapoh kata ka batsha, ka la long da kajuh ka jingtrei. U la thaw ruh ka ïing ïa ka khun u Pharaoh (ïa kaba u Solomon u la shim ban long ka tnga,) kum kane ka batsha.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kine baroh ki long da ki maw barem, ki maw kiba la shniah keiñ, kat kum ka jingthew, ba la ot da ki kurat, shapoh bad shabar, naduh ka nongrim haduh satep, bad kumjuh naduh na shabar haduh ka kamra ka bakhraw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka nongrim ka la long da ki maw barem, ki maw bakhraw keiñ, ki maw ki bashiphew pruh bad ki maw ki baphra pruh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad shalor la long da ki maw barem, ki maw ba la shniah keiñ, kat kum ka jingthew, bad ki dieng Kedar.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ka kamra bakhraw baroh sawdong la don lai lynter ki maw ba la shniah, bad shilynter ki bim Kedar; kum kaba shapoh jong ka ïing U Trai, bad ka batsha jong kata ka ïing.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la phah shaw ïa u Hiram na Tyros.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Une u la long u khun kawei ka riewkynthei na ka jaid Naphtali, bad u kpa jong u, u la long u briew na Tyros, u nongthaw rnong; bad la pyndap ïa u da ka jingstad bad ka jingshemphang bad ka buit ruh, ban thaw ka jingthaw baroh ha ka tama. Bad u la wan ha u syiem Solomon, bad u la trei ïa ka kam jong u baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba u la thaw ïa kita ar tylli ki rishot tama khatphra pruh ka jingjrong uwei uwei: bad u ksai khat-ar pruh u la kot sawdong ïa ki uwei uwei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la thaw ar tylli ki khlieh da ka tama ba la saiñ, ïa ka ban buh halor ki kliar kita ki rishot: ka jingjrong kawei ka khlieh ka la long san pruh, bad ka jingjrong kata kawei ka khlieh, san pruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> La don ki jar da ki jingthaw bapher bapher, bad ki pansngiat da ki kynjri, ïa kita ki khlieh kiba la don halor ki kliar kita ki rishot; hynñiew tylli ïa kawei ka khlieh, bad hynñiew tylli ïa kata kawei ka khlieh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta u la thaw ïa kita ki rishot; bad la don ar tylli ki lynter baroh sawdong halor kata ka jingthain jar, ban tap ïa kita ki khlieh kiba halor ki kliar kita ki rishot: bad kumta u la leh ïa kata kawei ka khlieh ruh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kita ki khlieh te kiba la don halor ki kliar kita ki rishot ha ka batsha ki la long ha ka dur 'tiew Lili, saw pruh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad la don ki khlieh nalor ruh ha kita ki ar tylli ki rishot, hajan ka pdeng kaba ha syndah kata ka jingthain jar: bad ki soh Pong ki la long arspah tylli lynter lynter baroh sawdong kata kawei pat ka khlieh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la pynïeng ïa kita ki rishot ha ka batsha ka templ: u la pynïeng te ïa u rishot kamon, bad u la kyrteng ïa u, “u Jakhin”: bad u la pynïeng ïa u rishot kadiang, bad u la kyrteng ïa u, “u Boas”.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ha ki kliar ki rishot la don ka jingtrei dur Lili: kumta la pyndep ïa ki kam kita ki rishot.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka duriaw ba la saiñ, shiphew pruh na rmiang sha rmiang, pyllun sawdong, bad ka jingjrong jong ka, ka la long san pruh: bad u ksai, laiphew pruh u kot baroh sawdong ïa ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te hapoh ka rmiang jong ka baroh sawdong la don ki shrong kiba baroh sawdong ïa ka, shiphew tylli shi pruh shi pruh, kiba tawiar sawdong ïa kata ka duriaw: ïa kita ki shrong la saiñ ar kyrdan, haba la saiñ ïa ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka la shong halor khat-ar tylli ki masi dab, lai tylli ki khmih shaphang shatei, bad lai tylli ki khmih shaphang sepngi, bad lai tylli ki khmih shaphang shathie, bad lai tylli ki khmih shaphang mihngi: bad ïa kata ka duriaw la pynshong halor jong ki, bad ki bynta kiba shadien jong ki baroh ki la long shapoh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ka long shi khup ka jingrben, bad ïa ka rmiang jong ka, la thaw kum ka rmiang ka khuri, kum u syntiew Lili; ka la ngiam ar hajar bath.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la thaw shiphew tylli ki jingpynshong dabor da ka tama; saw pruh la long ka lynter kawei ka jingpynshong, bad saw pruh ka pyngkiang jong ka, bad lai pruh ka jingjrong jong ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ka jingthaw ïa kita ki jingpynshong ka la long kumne: ki la don ki rmiang; bad la don ki rmiang hapdeng ki jingkyrshan:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ha kita ki rmiang kiba hapdeng kita ki jingkyrshan la don ki sing, ki masi dab, bad ki Kherub; bad halor kita ki jingkyrshan ka la long kumjuh sha khlieh: bad hapoh kita ki sing bad ki masi dab la don ki jingthaw shrong ba la sdien.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad kawei kawei ka jingpynshong ka la don saw tylli ki shalyntem tama, bad ki nar kali tama: bad ki saw kjat jong ka ki la don tyrpeng: hapoh ka dabor la don ki tyrpeng ba la saiñ, lem bad ki shrong ha krung kawei kawei.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ka shyntur jong ka hapoh ka khlieh bad shalor ka la long shi pruh: bad ka shyntur jong ka, ka la long kaba pyllun ha ka rukom ka jingpynshong, shi pruh shiteng: bad halor ka shyntur jong ka ruh la don ki jingot dur, bad ki rmiang jong ki, ki la long kiba sawdong, ym kiba pyllun.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te kita ki saw tylli ki shalyntem ki la don hapoh ki rmiang; bad ki nar kali jong ki shalyntem ki la don ha ka jingpynshong: bad ka jingjrong jong kawei ka shalyntem ka la long shi pruh shiteng.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ka jingthaw kita ki shalyntem ka la long kumba thaw ïa ki shalyntem kali: ki nar kali jong ki, ki dieng kyrwiang jong ki, ki diengphna jong ki, bad ki shaka jong ki, ki la long baroh phar kiba la saiñ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad la don saw tylli ki tyrpeng ha ki saw tylli ki dong jong kawei kawei ka jingpynshong: kita ki tyrpeng jong ka ki la long na ka jingpynshong hi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ha khlieh jong kata ka jingpynshong la don ka ryndang bapyllun shiteng pruh ka jingjrong: bad ha khlieh jong ka jingpynshong ki kti jong ka bad ki rmiang jong ka ki la long na kajuh hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te halor ki sla'ti jong ka bad halor ki rmiang jong ka u la ot dur ki Kherub, ki sing, bad ki dieng Tlai, katba kum ka jaka ha kawei kawei, lem bad ki shrong baroh sawdong.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kum ha kane ka rukom, u la thaw ïa kita ki shiphew tylli ki jingpynshong: baroh ki la don kawei ka jingsaiñ, kawei ka jingthew, bad kawei ka dur.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u la thaw shiphew tylli ki dabor rnong: kawei ka dabor ka ngiam sawphew bath: bad kawei kawei ka dabor ka long saw pruh: bad halor kawei kawei na kita ki shiphew tylli ki jingpynshong kawei ka dabor.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kita ki jingpynshong, san tylli shaphang kamon jong ka ïing, bad san tylli shaphang kadiang jong ka ïing: bad u la buh ïa kata ka duriaw shaphang kamon jong ka ïing, shaphang mihngi lam shathie.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u Hiram u la thaw ïa ki dabor, bad ïa ki siang, bad ïa ki khuri. Kumta, u Hiram u la pyndep ïa kaba trei ka kam baroh kaba u la trei na ka bynta u syiem Solomon ha ka ïing U Trai:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> kita ar tylli ki païa, bad ki ar tylli ki khuri jong ki khlieh kiba ha kliar jong kita ki païa; bad kita ar tylli ki jingthain jar ban tap ïa kita ki ar tylli ki khuri jong ki khlieh kiba ha kliar ki païa;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> bad kita ki sawspah tylli ki soh Pong ïa kita ki ar tylli ki jingthain jar; ar lynter ki soh Pong ïa kawei kawei ka jingthain jar, ban tap ïa ki ar tylli ki khuri jong ki khlieh kiba halor ki païa;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad kita ki shiphew tylli ki jingpynshong, bad ki shiphew tylli ki dabor halor kita ki jingpynshong;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad kata kawei ka duriaw, bad kita ki khat-ar ki masi dab hapoh kata ka duriaw;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> bad kita ki khiew, bad ki siang, bad ki khuri: bad ki kynja pliang baroh keiñ kiba u Hiram u la thaw ïa u syiem Solomon, ha ka ïing U Trai, ki la long da ka rnong baphyrnai.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ha ka madan Jordan u syiem u la saiñ ïa ki, ha kata ka 'dewbyrtha kaba hapdeng ka Sukkoth bad ka Sarethan.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te u Solomon um shym thew shuh ïa kita ki kynja pliang baroh, namar ba ki la bun than: ka jingthew ïa ka tama ym lah tip shuh.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad u Solomon u la thaw ïa kita ki kynja pliang baroh kiba ha ïing U Trai: ka duwan ksiar, bad kata ka miej ksiar ha kaba la don ki 'pu pyni;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad kita ki dieng pynïeng sharak da ka ksiar banylla, san tylli shaphang kamon, bad san tylli shaphang kadiang, ha khmat ka orakl; bad ki syntiew, bad ki sharak, bad ki nap, kiba da ka ksiar;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad ki bati, bad ki jinglur sharak, bad ki khuri, bad ki siang, bad ki pliang dieng, da ka ksiar banylla; bad ki kopja ksiar ïa ki jingkhang ka ïing kaba kham shapoh, ka jaka kyntang tam keiñ, bad ïa ka jingkhang ka ïing, kata jong ka templ.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Kumne la pyndep ïa ka kam baroh kaba u syiem Solomon u la thaw ha ka ïing U Trai. Bad u Solomon u la wallam hapoh ïa kita kiei kiei kiba u kpa jong u, u Dabid u la pynkyntang, ka rupa, ka ksiar, bad ki kynja pliang, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ki jaka kynshew jong ka ïing U Trai."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la ïalum lang ïa ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel, bad baroh ki nongïalam jong ki jaid, ki rangbah ki kpa ki khun Israel, sha u syiem Solomon ha Jerusalem, ban wallam noh artet ïa ka synduk ka jutang jong U Trai na ka shnong u Dabid, ka Seïon keiñ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki paidbah Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang ha u syiem Solomon, ha kata Ka Jingkhawai Niam ha u 'nai Ethanim, kata, u bnai u bahynriew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh ki ïawan, bad ki lyngdoh ki la ïarah ïa kata ka synduk.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la wallam noh ïa ka synduk U Trai, bad ka ïingjaiñ jong ka jingïaseng, bad ki kynja pliang bakhuid baroh kiba ha kata ka ïingjaiñ; ïa kine keiñ ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la wallam noh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u syiem Solomon bad baroh u paidlang Israel, uba la ïalum lang ha u, u la don bad u ha khmat kata ka synduk, ki ïakñia ïa ki langbrot bad ki masi ki bym lah ong shuh lymne kheiñ ba bun than eh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki lyngdoh te ki la pynrung ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ha la ka jaka, sha ka orakl jong kata ka ïing, sha ka bakyntang tam keiñ, hapoh ki thapniang ki Kherub.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba ki Kherub ki la pyiar ïa ki thapniang baroh ar halor ka jaka jong kata ka synduk, bad ki Kherub ki la tap ïa kata ka synduk bad ki dieng jingbah jong ka nalor.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kita ki dieng jingbah ki la jrong ba lah ban ïohi ïa ki tduh jong kita ki dieng jingbah na ka jaka kyntang ha khmat kata ka orakl; hynrei, ym ïohi ïa ki na shabar: hangta te ki don, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ei ei ruh em ym don ha kata ka synduk tang kita ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap kiba u Moses u la buh hangta ha Horeb, ha kaba U Trai u la pynlong ka jutang bad ki khun Israel, mynba ki la wan noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki lyngdoh ki la mih noh na kata ka jaka kyntang, u lyoh u la pyndap ïa ka ïing U Trai,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> katba ki lyngdoh kim lah ïeng shuh ban trei, namar uta u lyoh: naba ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa kata ka ïing U Trai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la kren, “U Trai u la ong ba un shong ha u lyoh barben.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga shisha nga la tei ka ïing ïa me ban shong, ka jaka ïa me ban shongneh junom.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u syiem u la phai la ka khmat sawdong, bad u la kyrkhu ïa uta u paidbah ki Israel baroh: bad u paidbah ki Israel baroh u ïeng.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei jong ki Israel, uba la kren da la ka shyntur ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad u la pyndep ïa ka da la ka kti, u da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ‘Naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la wallam noh ïa u paidbah jong nga – ki Israel – na Ijipt, ngam shym la jied kano kano ka shnong na ki jaid Israel baroh ban tei ïa ka ïing, ba ka kyrteng jong nga kan ïoh long hangta; hynrei, nga la jied ïa u Dabid ban long halor u paidbah jong nga, ki Israel.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka la don ha ka dohnud u Dabid u kpa jong nga ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la ong ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, ‘Kumba ka la don ha ka dohnud jong me ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, me la leh bha keiñ ba kane ka la don ha ka dohnud jong me:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> la kumta ruh, men ym tei ïa kata ka ïing; hynrei, u khun jong me u ban mih noh na ka syngkai jong me, uta un sa tei ïa kata ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynskhem ïa la ka ktien kaba u la kren; naba nga la ïeng ha ka jaka u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad nga shong halor ka khet Israel, kumba U Trai u la kular, bad nga la tei ïa kata ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad hangta nga la buh ka jaka ïa kata ka synduk, ha kaba don ka jutang U Trai, kaba u la pynlong bad ki kpa jong ngi, mynba u la wallam noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Solomon u la ïeng ha khmat ka duwan U Trai ha khmat u paidbah Israel baroh, bad u la rah ïa la ki kti sha bneng:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u la ong ruh, “A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ym don Blei kum ma me, ha bneng sha jrong, lane ha ka khyndew shapoh; uba sumar ïa ka jutang bad ka jingisynei bad la ki shakri, kiba ïaid ha khmat jong me da ka dohnud jong ki baroh:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> uba la sumar bad la u shakri u Dabid u kpa jong nga ïa kata kaba me la kular ha u: me la kren ruh da la ka shyntur, bad me la pyndep da la ka kti, kumba ha kane ka sngi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mynta te, A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, to sumar bad la u shakri u Dabid u kpa jong nga ïa kata kaba me la kular ha u, me da ong, ‘Kan ym duh briew ïa me ha khmat jong nga ban shong halor ka khet Israel; tang ba ki khun jong me kin sumar ïa la ka lynti, ban ïaid ha khmat jong nga kumba me la ïaid ha khmat jong nga.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata te, A U Blei ki Israel, nga duwai, to kan long shisha ka ktien jong me, kaba me la kren ha u shakri jong me u Dabid u kpa jong nga.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Hynrei shisha shisha, U Blei un shong sah ma ha ka pyrthei? ha khmih, ka bneng bad ka bneng jong ki bneng kim lah ban ngiam ïa me; ine i ïing lei lei i katno eh iba nga la tei!",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Pynban, to khmih ha ka jingduwai u shakri jong me, bad ha ka jingkyrpad jong u, A Trai U Blei jong nga, ban shahshkor ïa ka jingpyrta bad ka jingduwai kaba u shakri jong me u duwai ha khmat jong me ha kane ka sngi:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ba ki khmat jong me kin peit sha kane ka ïing mynmiet bad mynsngi, sha ka jaka ïa kaba me la ong, ‘Ka kyrteng jong nga kan long hangta’: ban shahshkor ïa ka jingduwai ba u shakri jong me un duwai sha kane ka jaka.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad to sngew ïa ka jingkyrpad u shakri jong me, bad ki jong ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba kin duwai sha kane ka jaka: to men sngew ruh ha bneng ka jaka shongneh jong me; bad haba me sngew, to map.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Lada u briew u leh palat ïa la u paramarjan, bad ba la buh ka jingsmai halor jong u ban pynsmai ïa u, bad u wan smai ha khmat ka duwan jong me ha kane ka ïing:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ynda kumta, to sngew ma me ha bneng, bad to leh, bad to bishar ïa la ki shakri, da pynrem ïa u bymman, ban pynhap ïa ka lynti jong u ha ka khlieh jong u hi; da pynksan de ïa u bahok, ban ai ha u katba kum ka hok jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Haba ki briew jong me ki Israel ki shah jop ha khmat u nongshun, namar ba ki la leh pop ïa me; bad lada kin phai pat sha me, bad kin phla ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad ki duwai bad ki kyrpad ha me ha kane ka ïing:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> te to sngew ma me ha bneng, bad to map ïa ka pop ki briew jong me ki Israel, bad to wallam pat ïa ki sha ka ri kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ki.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Haba la khang khop ïa ka bneng, bad ym don slap shuh, namar ki la leh pop ïa me; lada ki duwai sha kane ka jaka, bad ki phla ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad ki phai na la ka pop, haba me pynjynjar ïa ki:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> te to sngew ma me ha bneng, bad to map ïa ka pop ki shakri jong me, bad ka jong ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba me hikai ïa ki, ïa ka lynti ka babha ha kaba ki dei ban ïaid; bad to phah ruh ïa u slap ha ka ri jong me, kaba me la ai ha ki briew jong me ban long ka ri kynti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> “Lada jia 'nemsniew ha ka ri, lada jia ka jingïapkhlam, lada jia kaba ïap-ïong, kaba bthuh, u puit kluiñ lane u puit khlam; lada u nongshun jong ki u ker kut ïa ki ha ka ri ki khyrdop jong ki; la kano kano ka jingshitom, kano kano ka jingpang;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> kano kano ka jingduwai bad ka jingkyrpad ba pynlong da uno uno u briew, lane da ki briew jong me ki Israel baroh, uba tip marwei marwei ïa ka jingshitom la ka jong ka dohnud, bad u rah ïa la ki kti sha kane ka ïing:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> te to sngew ma me ha bneng ka jaka shongneh jong me, bad to map, bad to leh, bad to ai ha u briew baroh katba kum ki lynti jong u baroh, uba ka dohnud jong u me tip; (naba me, tang ma me hi keiñ, me tip ïa ka dohnud ki khun bynriew baroh;)",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ba kin dup sheptieng ïa me baroh ki sngi ba ki im ha kata ka ri kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ngi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “Shaphang u nongwei ruh, u bymdei na ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba u wan na ka ri kaba jngai na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong me;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> (naba kin sa bna ïa ka kyrteng bakhraw jong me, bad ïa ka kti badonbor jong me, bad ïa ka ksang'ti bakner jong me;) te haba u wan duwai sha kane ka ïing;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> to sngew ma me ha bneng ka jaka shongneh jong me, bad to leh baroh katba kum ka jingkyrpad uta u nongwei ha me; ba ki kynja bynriew ka pyrthei baroh kin tip ïa ka kyrteng jong me, ban sheptieng ïa me, kumba leh ki briew jong me ki Israel, bad ba kin tip ba ïa kane ka ïing kaba nga la tei la khot da ka kyrteng jong me.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Lada ki briew jong me ki leit sha ka thma bad u nongshun jong ki, da kano kano ka lynti ba men phah ïa ki, bad kin duwai ha U Trai sha ka shnong kaba me la jied, bad sha ka ïing kaba nga la tei ïa ka kyrteng jong me:",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> te to sngew ma me ha bneng ïa ka jingduwai jong ki bad ka jingkyrpad jong ki, bad to pynïeng ïa ka hok jong ki.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> “Lada kin leh pop ïa me, (naba ym don briew u bym ju leh pop,) bad men bitar bad ki, bad aiti noh ïa ki ha u nongshun, ba kumta un ring mraw ïa ki sha ka ri u nongshun, jngai ne hajan;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> pynban, lada kin pyrkhat ïa lade ha kata ka ri sha kaba la ring mraw ïa ki, bad kin phai pat, bad kin kyrpad ha me ha ka ri kita kiba la ring mraw ïa ki, ki ïa-ong, ‘Ngi la leh pop, bad ngi la leh mutlop, bad ngi la leh bymman ruh’;",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> lada kin phai ha me da ka dohnud jong ki baroh bad da ka mynsiem jong ki baroh ha kata ka ri ki nongshun jong ki, kiba la ring mraw ïa ki, bad kin duwai ha me sha ka ri jong ki, kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ki, kane ka shnong kaba me la jied, bad kane ka ïing kaba nga la tei ïa ka kyrteng jong me:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> te to sngew ma me ïa ka jingduwai jong ki bad ki jingkyrpad jong ki ha bneng ka jaka shongneh jong me, bad to pynïeng ïa ka hok jong ki;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad to map ïa ki briew jong me kiba la leh pop ïa me, bad ïa ki jingpalat jong ki baroh ha kiba ki la leh palat ïa me; bad to ai kin shem jingisynei ha khmat kita kiba la ring mraw ïa ki, ba kita kin leh isynei ïa ki:",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> namar ki long ki briew jong me, bad ka bynta jong me, kiba me la wallam noh na ri Ijipt, napdeng ka lawar ding nar:",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> ba ki khmat jong me kin peit sha ka jingkyrpad u shakri jong me, bad sha ka jingkyrpad ki Israel ki briew jong me, ïa ka ban shahshkor ïa ki ha kano kano ka por ba kin pyrta ha me.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Naba me la pynkyrpang ïa ki napdeng ki briew ka pyrthei baroh ban long ka bynta jong me, kumba me la kren da ka kti u Moses u shakri jong me, mynba me la wallam ïa ki kpa jong ngi na Ijipt, A Trai uba U Blei.”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te haba u Solomon u la wai noh kaba duwai kane ka jingduwai bad ka jingkyrpad baroh ha U Trai, u la ïeng na khmat ka duwan U Trai, na kaba dem la ki khohsiew bad la ki kti ba la kner sha bneng.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te u la ïeng, bad u la kyrkhu ïa ka jingïaseng ki Israel baroh da ka ktien bajam, u da ong,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> “To long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, uba la ai ka jingshongthait ha la ki briew ki Israel, katba kum kaba u la kular baroh: ym shym la duh ei kawei ka ktien na ka jingkular babha jong u baroh, kaba u la kular da ka kti u Moses u shakri jong u.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> To U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi un long lem bad ngi, kumba u la long bad ki kpa jong ngi: to wat ai un iehnoh ïa ngi, lymne lyndet ïa ngi:",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> ba un lah pyndem ïa ki dohnud jong ngi sha u, ban ïaid ha ki lynti jong u baroh, bad ban rakhe ïa ki hukum jong u, bad ïa ki aiñ jong u, bad ïa ki jingbishar jong u de, kiba u la hukum ïa ki kpa jong ngi.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Bad to shah ba kine ki ktien jong nga, da kiba nga la kyrpad ha khmat U Trai, kin long hajan U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi mynsngi bad mynmiet, ba un pynïeng ïa ka hok u shakri jong u, bad ïa ka hok ki briew jong u ki Israel, katba donkam man la ka sngi:",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> ba ki kynja bynriew ka pyrthei baroh kin ïoh tip ba U Trai keiñ, uba long U Blei: ym don shuh uwei pat.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> To ai, namar kata, ba ki dohnud jong phi kin long ki bajanai bad U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi, bad ïaid ha ki aiñ jong u, bad ban rakhe ïa ki hukum jong u, kumba ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Te u syiem, lem bad ki Israel baroh bad u, ki la kñia ka jingkñia ha khmat U Trai.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Te u Solomon u la ai ban long ka jingkñia ki jingainguh pynïasuk, kaba u la ainguh ha U Trai, arphew ar hajar ki masi dab, bad shispah arphew hajar ki langbrot. Kumta u syiem bad ki khun Israel baroh ki la pynkyntang ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Ha kajuh ka sngi, u syiem u la pynkyntang ïa ka pdeng ka phyllaw kaba ha khmat ka ïing U Trai; naba hangta u la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ka jingainguh bam, bad ïa ka khleiñ ka jingainguh pynïasuk: namar ka duwan rnong kaba ha khmat U Trai kam biang ban pdiang ïa ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ka jingainguh bam, bad ïa ka khleiñ ka jingainguh pynïasuk.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Kumta, u Solomon ha kata ka por, u la pynlong ïa kata ka jingkhawai ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong ngi, bad ki Israel baroh lem bad u, u paidbah babun byllien, na kaba bsut sha Hamath haduh ka wah Ijipt, hynñiew sngi bad hynñiew sngi, khatsaw sngi keiñ.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Ha ka sngi ka baphra u la phah noh ïa u paidbah, ki te ki la kyrkhu ïa u syiem, bad ki la leit sha la ki ïingjaiñ da ka dohnud bakmen bad basngewbha namar kata ka babha baroh kaba U Trai u la pyni ha u Dabid u shakri jong u, bad ha ki Israel ki briew jong u."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda u Solomon u la lah dep kaba tei ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ka ïing u syiem, bad ïa ka jingkwah u Solomon baroh kaba u sngewbha ban leh,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Trai u la paw ha u Solomon ha ka ba-ar sien, kumba u la lah paw ha u ha Gibeon.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u, “Nga la shahshkor ïa ka jingduwai jong me bad ïa ka jingkyrpad jong me, ba me la pynlong ha khmat jong nga: nga la pynkyntang ïa kane ka ïing, kaba me la tei, ïa ka ban buh ïa ka kyrteng jong nga hangta ha la ka rta; te ki khmat jong nga bad ka dohnud jong nga kin long hangta borabor.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ma me ruh, lada men ïaid ha khmat jong nga, kumba u Dabid u kpa jong me u la ïaid, ha ka jingjanai ka dohnud, bad ha ka jingbeit, ban leh baroh katba nga la hukum ma nga ïa me, bad men rakhe ïa ki aiñ bad ki jingbishar jong nga;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> nga te ngan pynskhem ïa ka khet ka hima jong me halor ki Israel junom: kat kumba nga la kular ha u Dabid u kpa jong me, da kaba ong, ‘Kan ym duh briew ïa me halor ka khet ki Israel.’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, lada phin phai noh na kaba bud ïa nga, ma phi lane ki khun jong phi, bad phim rakhe ïa ki hukum bad ki aiñ jong nga kiba nga la buh ha khmat jong phi, hynrei, phin leit shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei, bad mane ïa ki:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> te ngan ot noh ïa ki Israel na ka ri kaba nga la ai ha ki; bad ïa kane ka ïing, kaba nga la pynkyntang ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, ngan shop noh na khmat jong nga; bad ki Israel kin long ka jingkhmih bad ka jingkynshi hapdeng ki kynja bynriew baroh:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad la kane ka ïing ka jrong katta katta, pynban, uwei uwei baroh uba ïaid najan jong ka, un kyndit, bad un kynshi; bad kin ong, ‘Balei ba U Trai u la leh kumne ïa kane ka ri, bad ïa kane ka ïing?’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki te kin ïathuh, ‘Namar ba ki la lyndet ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, uba la wallam noh ïa ki kpa jong ki na ka ri Ijipt, bad ki la sohbah ïa kiwei pat ki blei, bad ki la mane ïa ki, bad ki la shakri ïa ki: namar kata, U Trai u la pynhap halor jong ki ïa kane ka jingsniew baroh.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha ka bakut ki arphew snem, ha kiba u Solomon u la tei ïa kita ki ïing baroh ar, ka ïing U Trai, bad ka ïing u syiem,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> (te u Hiram u syiem ka Tyros u la taïar ïa u Solomon ki dieng Kedar bad ki dieng Kseh, lem bad ka ksiar, kat kum ka jingkwah jong u baroh,) ynda kumta, u Solomon u la ai ha u Hiram arphew tylli ki nongbah ha ka ri Galilaïa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Hiram u la mih na Tyros ban leit khmih ïa kita ki nongbah kiba u Solomon u la lah ai ïa u, bad um sngewbha bad ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u la ong, “Ki nongbah aïu kum kine ba me la ai ïa nga, ko para?” Bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ki “ka ri Kabul”, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Hiram u la phah ha u syiem hynriewphew talent ksiar.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kane ka long ka daw ba u syiem Solomon u la pynmih ïa kita ki paid, ïa ka ban tei ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa la ka jong ka ïing, bad ka Millo, bad ïa ka kynroh ka Jerusalem, bad ka Hasor, bad ka Megiddo, bad ka Geser.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Pharaoh u syiem ka Ijipt u la lah leit kiew, bad u la jop ïa ka Geser, bad u la thang ïa ka da ka ding, bad u la pynïap ïa ki Kanaan kiba shong ha kata ka nongbah, bad u la ai ïa ka, kum ka bynta ha la ka khun, ka tnga u Solomon.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Solomon u la tei ïa ka Geser, bad ïa ka Beth-horon kaba harum,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ka Baalath, bad ka Tadmor ha ka ri khlaw, ha ka ri,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ïa ki nongbah jingkynshew baroh kiba u Solomon u don, bad ïa ki nongbah ïa ki kali jong u, bad ki nongbah ïa ki nongshong kulai jong u, bad kata kaba u Solomon u la kwah ban tei sngewbha ha Jerusalem, bad ha Lebanon, bad ha ka ri ka jingsynshar jong u baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Shaphang kita ki briew baroh ïa kiba la pynsah na ki Amor, ki Hit, ki Peris, ki Hib, bad ki Jebus, ki bym shym dei na ki khun Israel;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ïa ki khun jong ki, kiba la pynsah hadien jong ki ha ka ri, kiba ki khun Israel kim lah ban pynduh khoit ïa ki, na kita keiñ, u Solomon u la pynmih ïa ki khar paid kum ki mraw, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, na ki khun Israel, u Solomon um shym pynlong mraw, hynrei, ki la long ki nongïapom, bad ki shakri jong u, bad ki bakhraw batri jong u, bad ki kaptan jong u, bad ki rangbah ki kali ïapom jong u, bad ki nongshong kulai jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kine ki la long ki rangbah bakhraw kiba halor ka jingtrei u Solomon, sanspah sanphew ngut, kiba la synshar halor ki briew kiba la trei ha kata ka jingtrei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ka khun u Pharaoh ka la leit mih na ka shnong u Dabid sha la ka ïing kaba u Solomon u la lah tei ïa ka: ynda kumta, u la tei ïa ka Millo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te lai sien shi snem u Solomon u ju ainguh da ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk halor ka duwan kaba u la tei ha U Trai, u la thang ka jingiwbih da kita, halor ka duwan kaba ha khmat U Trai. Kumta, u la pyndep ïa ka ïing.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la thaw ki lieng ha Esion-geber, kaba hajan ka Eloth, harud ka Duriaw Basaw, ha ka ri Edom.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Hiram u la phah ïa la ki shakri ha kita ki lieng, kiba nang shaphang ka duriaw, lem bad ki shakri u Solomon.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki la leit poi sha Ophir, bad nangta, ki la wallam ksiar sanspah arphew talent, bad ki wallam ïa ka ha u syiem Solomon."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ka syiem Sheba ka la ïohsngew ïa ka nam u Solomon shaphang ka kyrteng U Trai, ka la wan ban tynjuh ïa u da ki jingkylli kiba eh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka la wan sha Jerusalem bad shibun bah ki nongbud, lem bad ki ut kiba kit ki jingiwbih, bad shikatdei eh ka ksiar, bad ki mawkordor: te haba ka la poi ha u Solomon, ka la ïakren bad u shaphang kiei kiei baroh kiba ha ka dohnud jong ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Solomon u la ïathuh ha ka, ïa ki jingkylli jong ka baroh: ym shym don kaei kaei ruh kaba la buhrieh na u syiem kaba um shym ïathuh ha ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda ka syiem Sheba ka la ïohi ïa ka jingstad u Solomon baroh, bad ïa ka ïing kaba u la lah tei,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ka jingbam ka miej jong u, bad kaba shong ki shakri jong u, bad kaba ïeng ki myntri jong u, bad ki jaiñkup jaiñsem jong ki, bad ki rangbah khuri jong u, bad ïa ka lynti jong u da kaba u leit kiew sha ïing U Trai; kam shym tipbriew ei ei shuh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ka la ong ha u syiem, “Ka la long ka jingbna kaba shisha kaba nga la ïohsngew ha ka ri jong nga hi shaphang ki jingleh jong me, bad shaphang ka jingstad jong me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, ngam shym la ngeit ïa kita ki ktien, haduh ba nga la wan, bad ki khmat jong nga ki la lah ïohi ïa ka: te, ha khmih, shiteng ruh ym shym la ïathuh ha nga: ka jingstad bad ka jingmanbha jong me ki palat ïa ka nam kaba nga la ïoh bna.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Suk ki briew jong me, suk kine ki shakri, kiba ïeng borabor ha khmat jong me, kiba ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad jong me.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai U Blei jong me, uba ieit ïa me, ban buh ïa me halor ka khet ki Israel: namar U Trai u ieit junom ïa ki Israel, namar kata, u la pynlong syiem ïa me ban bishar bad ban leh hok.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka la ai ha u syiem shispah arphew ki talent ksiar, bad ki jingiwbih shibun eh, bad ki mawkordor: ym shym la poi shuh ki jingiwbih ki ban bun kat kine kiba ka syiem Sheba ka la ai ha u syiem Solomon.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki lieng u Hiram ruh, kiba ju wallam ksiar na Ophir, ki la wallam na Ophir shibun bah ki dieng Almug bad ki mawkordor.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u syiem la thaw ki rishot da kita ki dieng Almug ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ka ïing u syiem, ki duitara ruh bad ki nebel ïa ki nongrwai: ym ju poi kum kita ki dieng Almug, lymne ym ju ïohi, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la ai ha ka syiem Sheba ïa ka jingkwah jong ka baroh, kaei kaei ruh kat kaba ka la pan, nalor kaba u Solomon u la ai sngewbha ha ka kum u syiem. Kumta, ka la leit wan noh bad ka la leit sha la ka ri hi, ma ka bad ki shakri jong ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ka jingthew ka ksiar kaba la poi ha u Solomon shi snem shi snem ka long hynriewspah hynriewphew hynriew ki talent ksiar,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> nalor kaba ki nongkhaïi ki ju wallam, bad ka jingkhaïi ki mahajon, bad na ki syiem baroh jong ki kynja bynriew baïakhleh, bad na ki nongsynshar ka ri.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u syiem Solomon u la thaw arspah ki 'tiehbah da ka ksiar ba shu shoh: hynriewspah shekel ka ksiar ka leit ha kawei ka 'tiehbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la thaw laispah tylli ki stieh da ka ksiar ba shu shoh; shi ser shiteng ka ksiar ka leit ha kawei ka stieh; bad u syiem u la buh ïa ki ha ka ïing ka khlaw Lebanon.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U syiem u la thaw ruh ïa ka khet bakhraw da ki bniat hati, bad u la suit ïa ka da ka ksiar ka babha tam.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kata ka khet ka la don hynriew tylli ki kyrdan, bad ka khlieh jong kata ka khet ka la long pyllun na shadien: bad la don ki jingshan baroh ar liang ka jingshong, bad ar tylli ki sing kiba ïeng hajan kita ki jingshan.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad khat-ar tylli ki sing ki la ïeng hangta baroh ar liang halor kita ki hynriew ki kyrdan: ym ju thaw kum kata ha kano kano ka hima.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad baroh ki khuri dih jingdih u syiem Solomon ki la long da ka ksiar, bad baroh ki khuri ka ïing jong ka khlaw Lebanon ki la long da ka ksiar banylla: kawei ruh kam shym long da ka rupa; ym ju ñiewkor ei ei ïa ka ha ki sngi u Solomon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba u syiem u la don ha duriaw ki lieng Tarshish lem bad ki lieng u Hiram: shi sien ha ki lai snem ki lieng Tarshish ki ju poi, ki ïawallam ka ksiar, bad ka rupa, ki bniat hati, bad ki huleng, bad ki klew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, u syiem Solomon u la palat ïa ki syiem ka pyrthei baroh ha ka spah bad ha ka jingstad.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad baroh ka pyrthei ka la wad ïa ka khmat u Solomon, ban ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad jong u, kaba U Blei u la buh ha ka dohnud jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la wallam u briew baroh ïa la ka jingai sngewbha, ki pliang rupa, bad ki pliang ksiar, bad ki jaiñkup, bad ki jingkieng atiar, bad ki jingiwbih, ki kulai, bad ki khashor, da ka jingkheiñ man la ka snem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Solomon u la lum lang ïa ki kali bad ki nongshong kulai: bad u la don shi hajar sawspah ki kali ïapom, bad khat-ar hajar ki nongshong kulai, kiba u la buh ha ki shnong ri kali, bad lem bad u syiem ha Jerusalem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u syiem u la pynlong ïa ka rupa ha Jerusalem kum ki maw, bad ïa ki dieng Kedar u la pynlong kum ïa ki dieng Dumbur kiba ha ri them, namar ba bun eh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki kulai kiba u Solomon u la don la wallam ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt; bad ki nongkhaïi u syiem ki la shim ïa ki da ki kynhun, kawei kawei ka kynhun ha la ka dor.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ka kali ka la wan kiew bad ka la mih noh na Ijipt hynriewspah shekel rupa, bad uwei u kulai shispah sanphew: bad kumta ïa ki syiem ki Hit baroh, bad ïa ki syiem ka Syria, ki la wallam ïa ki ha la ki kti."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la ieit shibun ki kynthei nongwei, nalor ka khun u Pharaoh, ki kynthei ki Moab, ki Ammon, ki Edom, ki Sidon, bad ki Hit;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na kita ki jaid bynriew shaphang kiba U Trai u la ong ha ki khun Israel, “Phin ym leit hapdeng jong ki, lymne kin ym wan hapdeng jong phi: naba shisha kin pynphai noh ïa ki dohnud jong phi sha ki blei jong ki”: ha kine, u Solomon u la snoh ka jingieit.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la don hynñiewspah ngut ki tnga, ki mahadei, bad laispah ngut ki tnga kliar: bad ki tnga jong u ki la pynphai noh ïa ka dohnud jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar ynda u Solomon u la tymmen, ki tnga jong u ki la pynphai noh ïa ka dohnud jong u sha kiwei pat ki blei: bad ka dohnud jong u kam shym long janai bad U Trai U Blei jong u, kumba la long ka dohnud u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar u Solomon u la bud ïa ka Ashtoreth ka blei ki Sidon, bad ïa u Milkom ka jingijli jong ki Ammon.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Solomon u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad um shym bud biang ïa U Trai, kumba leh u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Solomon u la tei ïa ka jaka bajrong ïa u Khemosh u jingijli ki Moab, ha u lum uba ha pyrshah Jerusalem, bad ïa u Molek ka jingijli ki khun u Ammon.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kumta u la leh ïa ki tnga nongwei jong u baroh, kiba ju thang jingiwbih bad ba kñia ïa ki blei jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai u la bitar ïa u Solomon, namar ba ka dohnud jong u ka la phai noh na U Trai, U Blei jong ki Israel, uba la paw ar sien ha u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u la lah hukum ïa u shaphang kane hi, ba un ym leit bud ïa kiwei pat ki blei: hynrei, um shym sumar ïa kata kaba U Trai u la hukum.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, U Trai u la ong ha u Solomon, “Namar ba kat kane ka long bad me, bad mem shym la sumar ïa ka jutang jong nga bad ïa ki aiñ jong nga, kiba nga la hukum ïa me, shisha ngan kad ïa ka hima na me, bad ngan ai ïa ka ha u shakri jong me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> La kumta ruh, ha ki sngi jong me ngan ym leh ïa ka, na ka bynta u Dabid u kpa jong me: hynrei, ngan kad noh ïa ka na ka kti u khun jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ngan ym kad ïa ka hima baroh; hynrei, ngan ai kawei ka jaid ha u khun jong me, na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong nga, bad na ka bynta ka Jerusalem kaba nga la jied.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U Trai u la pynmih u nongïaleh pyrshah ïa u Solomon, u Hadad u nong Edom: une u la long na ka jaid syiem ha Edom.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba mynba u Dabid u la don ha Edom, bad u Joab u kaptan u paidïapom u la leit kiew ban tep ïa kiba la pynïap, haba u la lah pynïap ïa u shynrang baroh ha Edom;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> (naba u Joab bad ki Israel baroh ki la sah hangta hynriew bnai, haduh ba u la pynduh noh ïa u shynrang baroh ha Edom;)",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> uta u Hadad u la phet ïap, ma u bad ki nong Edom ruh bad u ki shakri u kpa jong u, ïa ka ban leit sha Ijipt; myn haba u Hadad u dang khynnah eh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki la mih na Midian, bad ki la poi sha Paran: bad ki ïashim briew bad ki na Paran, bad ki la poi sha Ijipt, sha u Pharaoh u syiem ka Ijipt; uba la ai ka ïing ïa u, bad u la buh ka bam ruh ïa u, bad u la ai khyndew ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Hadad te u la shem ka jingsngewbha kaba khraw ha khmat u Pharaoh, kumta, u la pynbuh kurim ïa u bad ka para jong ka tnga jong u hi, ka para jong ka Tahpenis ka mahadei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka para ka Tahpenis ka la kha ïa u Genubath u khun jong u, ïa uba ka Tahpenis ka pyniehnoh buiñ ha ïing u Pharaoh: bad u Genubath u la don ha ïing u Pharaoh hapdeng ki khun shynrang u Pharaoh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u Hadad u la ïohsngew ha Ijipt ba u Dabid u la thiah lem bad la ki kpa, bad ba u Joab u kaptan u paidïapom u la ïap, u Hadad u la ong ha u Pharaoh, “To shah ba ngan leit noh, ba ngan ïoh leit sha la ka jong ka ri.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la ong ha u, “Me kyrduh aïu bad nga, ha khmih, ba me wad ban leit sha la ka jong ka ri?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ei ei ruh em: la kumta to shah ba ngan leit la kumno kumno ruh.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Blei u la pynmih ïa uwei pat u nongïaleh pyrshah ïa u, u Reson, u khun u Eliada, uba la lah phet na la u kynrad u Hadadeser u syiem ka Sobah:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> te u la ïalum briew ha u, bad u la long u kaptan halor u paidbah, mynba u Dabid u la pynïap ïa kita na Sobah: te ki la leit sha Damaskos, bad ki la shong hangta, bad ki la synshar ha Damaskos.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u la long u nongïaleh pyrshah ïa ki Israel baroh ki sngi u Solomon, nalor ka jingpynjulor kaba u Hadad u la leh: bad u la isaitmet ïa ki Israel, bad u la synshar halor ka Syria.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, u nong Ephraim na Seredah, u shakri u Solomon, uba ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u “ka Seruah”, ka riewkynthei; u ruh, u la rah ïa la ka kti ban ïaleh ïa u syiem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kane te ka la long ka daw ba u la rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa u syiem: u Solomon u la tei ïa ka Millo, bad u la shna ïa kaba twa ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad uta u briew, u Jeroboam, u la long uba jur ka bor: te u Solomon u la ïohi ïa uta u samla ba u long uba minot, bad u la ai ha u ka jingsumar halor ka jingtrei baroh jong ka ïing u Joseph.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ha kata ka por, mynba u Jeroboam u la mih noh na Jerusalem, u Ahijah u nongïathuhlypa u nong Shilon u la shem ïa u ha lynti; te u Ahijah u la riam ïa lade da ki jaiñ thymmai; te kine ki ïadon tang ar ngut hi ha kata ka madan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Ahijah te u la shim ïa kata ka jaiñ thymmai kaba ha u, bad u la tar ïa ka khat-ar lyngkhot.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la ong ha u Jeroboam, “Shim ha me shiphew lyngkhot: naba kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Ha khmih, ngan kad ïa ka hima na ka kti u Solomon, bad ngan ai shiphew jaid ha me:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> (hynrei, ma u, un ïoh kawei ka jaid, na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong nga, bad na ka bynta ka Jerusalem, ka shnong kaba nga la jied na ki jaid Israel baroh:)",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> namar ba ki la lyndet ïa nga, bad ki la mane ïa ka Ashtoreth ka blei ki Sidon, ïa u Khemosh u blei ki Moab, bad ïa u Milkom u blei ki khun u Ammon; bad kim shym la ïaid ha ki lynti jong nga, ban leh ïa kata kaba dei ha ki khmat jong nga, bad ban sumar ïa ki aiñ bad ki jingbishar jong nga, kumba la leh u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ngan ym shim ïa ka hima baroh na ka kti jong u: hynrei, ngan pynlong syiem ïa u baroh ki sngi ka jingim jong u, na ka bynta u Dabid u shakri jong nga, uba nga la jied, namar ba u la sumar ïa ki hukum bad ïa ki aiñ jong nga:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> hynrei, ngan shim ïa kata ka hima na ka kti u khun jong u, bad ngan ai ïa ka ha me, ki shiphew jaid keiñ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ha u khun jong u ngan ai kawei ka jaid, ba u Dabid u shakri jong nga un ïoh ka sharak ha khmat jong nga borabor ha Jerusalem, kata ka shnong kaba nga la jied ban buh ïa la ka kyrteng hangta.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad ngan shim ïa me, bad men synshar katba kwah ka mynsiem jong me baroh, bad men long u syiem halor ki Israel.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te lada men shahshkor ïa kaba nga hukum ïa me baroh, bad men ïaid ha ki lynti jong nga, bad men leh ïa kata kaba dei ha ki khmat jong nga, ban sumar ïa ki aiñ bad ki hukum jong nga, kumba u Dabid u shakri jong nga u la leh; ngan long ryngkat bad me, bad ngan tei ïa me ka ïing kaba skhem, kumba nga la tei ïa u Dabid, bad ngan ai ïa ki Israel ha me.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad namar kane, ngan pynjynjar ïa u symbai u Dabid, hynrei, ym ha la ka rta.’ ”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Namar kata, u Solomon u la wad ban pynïap ïa u Jeroboam: hynrei, u Jeroboam u la ïeng, bad u la phet ïap sha Ijipt, sha u Shishak u syiem ka Ijipt, bad u la don ha Ijipt haduh ka jingïap u Solomon.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te kita kiwei ki kam u Solomon, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad baroh ka jingstad jong u, hato ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Kam u Solomon?",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad ka por ba u la synshar u Solomon ha Jerusalem halor ki Israel baroh ka long sawphew snem.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u Solomon u la thiah bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u: te u Rehoboam u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Rehoboam u la leit sha Shekhem: naba ki Israel baroh ki la wan sha Shekhem ban thung syiem ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat u la bna ïa kata, (naba u dang sah ha Ijipt, ha kaba u la phet ïap na khmat u syiem Solomon, bad u Jeroboam u la shong ha Ijipt,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ki la phah khot ïa u;) u Jeroboam bad u paidbah Israel baroh ki la wan, bad ki la ïakren ha u Rehoboam, ki da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “U kpa jong me u la pynlong khia ïa ka lyngkor jong ngi: mynta te men pynsting ïa ka jingpyntrei khia u kpa jong me, bad ka lyngkor bakhia jong u kaba u la buh halor jong ngi, te ngin sa nguh ïa me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Khie leit noh sa lai sngi, ynda kumta sa wan pat ha nga.” Kumta u paidbah u la leit noh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u syiem Rehoboam u la ïapyrkhat bad ki tymmen, kiba la ju ïeng ha khmat u Solomon u kpa jong u katba u dang im, u da ong, “Kumno phi pyni ïa nga ba ngan ai jubab ha une u paidbah?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki te ki la kren ha u, ki da ong, “Lada men long u shakri ïa une u paidbah ha kane ka sngi, bad men shakri ïa ki, bad men phai ktien ïa ki, bad men kren ki ktien ki babha ha ki, ki ruh kin long shakri ïa me junom.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u la lyndet ïa ka jingpyni ki tymmen kaba ki la ai ha u, bad u la ïapyrkhat bad ki samla kiba la ïasan ryngkat bad u, kiba ju ïeng ha khmat jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Kumno phi pyni, ba ngin ai jubab ha une u paidbah, uba la kren ha nga, u da ong, ‘To pynsting ïa ka lyngkor kaba u kpa jong me u la buh halor jong ngi?’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki samla kiba la ïasan ryngkat bad u ki la kren ha u, ki ïa-ong, “Kumne men ong ha une u paidbah uba la kren ha me, uba ong, ‘U kpa jong me u la pynkhia ïa ka lyngkor jong ngi, hynrei, to men kham pynsting ïa ka ha ngi;’ kumne keiñ men kren ha ki, ‘Ka 'tiduh jong nga ka kham khraw ban ïa ka syngkai u kpa jong nga.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mynta te kumba u kpa jong nga u la pynkit ïa phi da ka lyngkor kaba khia, nga ngan nang pyntam shuh ha ka lyngkor jong phi: u kpa jong nga u la pynshitom ïa phi da ki dieng sympat, hynrei, nga ngan pynshitom ïa phi da ki shabuk.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, u Jeroboam bad u paidbah baroh ki la ïawan ha u Rehoboam ha ka sngi ka balai, kumba la hukum u syiem, u da ong, “To wan ha nga ynda la lai sngi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u syiem u la phai ktien ha u paidbah da kaba eh, bad u la kyntait ïa ka jingpyni jong ki tymmen kaba ki la ai ha u;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u la kren ha ki kum ka jingpyni ki samla, u da ong, “U kpa jong nga u la pynkhia ïa ka lyngkor jong phi, hynrei, nga ngan nang pyntam shuh ïa ka lyngkor jong phi: u kpa jong nga u la pynshitom ïa phi da ki dieng sympat, hynrei, nga, ngan pynshitom ïa phi da ki shabuk.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u syiem um shym pynshahshkor ha uta u paidbah; namar ka la long ka kam ba la pynjia da U Trai, ba un ïoh pynskhem ïa la ka ktien, kaba U Trai u la kren da ka kti u Ahijah u nong Shilon ha u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba ki Israel ki la ïohi ba u syiem um pynshahshkor ha ki, u paidbah u la ïathuh ha u syiem, u da ong, “Ngi don bynta aïu ha u Dabid? lymne ngim don ka jingïoh ei ei ha u khun u Jesse: ïa, sha la ki ïingjaiñ, ko Israel; mynta te to khmih hi ïa la ka ïing, ko Dabid.” Kumta, ki Israel ki la leit noh sha la ki ïingjaiñ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita ki khun Israel kiba shong ha ki shnong Judah, u Rehoboam u la synshar halor jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Rehoboam u la phah ïa u Adoram, uba halor ka khajna; te ki Israel baroh ki la lynthem ïa u da ki maw, haduh ba u la ïap. Te u syiem Rehoboam u la pynkloi ban kiew ha la ka kali, ïa ka ban phet sha Jerusalem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, ki Israel ki la ïaleh pyrshah ïa ka ïing u Dabid, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba ki Israel baroh ki la ïohsngew ba u Jeroboam u la wan phai pat, ki la phah khot ïa u sha ka jingïaseng, bad ki la pynlong syiem ïa u halor ki Israel baroh: ym don ba bud ïa ka ïing u Dabid, hynrei, tang ka ïing Judah hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u Rehoboam u la wan poi sha Jerusalem, u la lum lang ïa ka ïing u Judah baroh, bad ïa ka jaid Benjamin, shispah phraphew hajar ki rangbah bakynsai, kiba la long ki rangbah ïapom, ban ïaleh thma ïa ka ïing Israel, ban pynphai pat ïa ka hima sha u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien na U Blei ka la wan ha u Shemaïah u briew jong U Blei, ka da ong,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “To kren ha u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon, u syiem ka Judah, bad ha ka ïing Judah bad Benjamin baroh, bad ha kita kiwei na u paidbah, to ong,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ‘Kumne ong U Trai: “Phin ym leit kiew, lymne ïaleh thma ïa ki para jong phi ki khun Israel: to leit phai noh uwei pa uwei sha la ïing; naba kane ka long na nga.” ’ ” Kumta, ki la shahshkor ïa ka ktien U Trai, haba ki la phai ki la leit noh, katba kum ka ktien U Trai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jeroboam u la tei ïa ka Shekhem ha ri lum Ephraim, bad u la shong ha ka; bad u la mih noh nangta, bad u la tei ïa ka Penuel.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Jeroboam u la ong ha la ka dohnud, “Mynta ka hima kan phai pat sha ka ïing u Dabid:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> lada une u paidbah un leit kiew ban kñia ha ka ïing U Trai ha Jerusalem, kumta ka dohnud une u paidbah kan phai pat sha u kynrad jong ki, sha u Rehoboam u syiem ka Judah keiñ; bad kin pynïap ïa nga, bad kin phai pat sha u Rehoboam u syiem ka Judah.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kata, u syiem u la ïapyrkhat, bad u la thaw ar tylli ki khun masi ksiar; bad u la ong ha ki, “Ka shitom eh ba phi leit kiew sha Jerusalem; ha khmih ki blei jong me, ko Israel, kiba la wallam ïa me na ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u la buh ïa uwei ha Bethel, bad ïa uta uwei u la buh ha Dan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad kane ka la wan long ka pop: naba u paidbah u la leit mane ha khmat uta uwei, wat haduh Dan.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la thaw ki ïing kita ki jaka bajrong, bad u la pynlong lyngdoh napdeng u paidbah baroh, ki bym da dei na ki khun u Lebi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Jeroboam u la pynlong Ka Jingkhawai Niam ha u bnai u baphra, ha ka bakhatsan sngi jong uta u bnai, kum Ka Jingkhawai Niam kaba don ha Judah, bad u la leit kiew sha ka duwan; kumta, u la leh ha Bethel, u da kñia ha kita ki khun masi kiba u la lah thaw: bad u la buh ha Bethel ïa kita ki lyngdoh ki jaka bajrong kiba u la lah thaw.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u la leit kiew ha ka duwan kaba u la lah thaw ha Bethel ha ka bakhatsan sngi u bnai u baphra, ha uta hi u bnai uba u la lah pyrkhat ha la ka dohnud: te u la pynlong Ka Jingkhawai Niam ïa ki khun Israel, bad u la leit kiew sha ka duwan, ban thang jingiwbih."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha khmih, la wan na Bethel u briew U Blei na Judah da ka ktien U Trai: u Jeroboam te u dang ïeng hajan ka duwan ban thang jingiwbih.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la pyrta ïa kata ka duwan da ka ktien U Trai, bad u la ong, “Ko duwan, duwan, kumne ong U Trai: ‘Ha khmih, yn kha u khun ha ka ïing u Dabid, yn kyrteng u Josaïah ïa u; halor jong pha un kñia ïa ki lyngdoh ki jaka bajrong kiba thang jingiwbih halor jong pha, bad kin thang shyieng briew halor jong pha.’ ”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ai ka dak ha kata kajuh ka sngi, u da ong, “Kane ka long ka dak kaba U Trai u la kren: ‘Ha khmih, yn pynkad ïa ka duwan, bad ïa ka dpei kaba halor jong ka yn theh noh.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u syiem u la ïohsngew ïa kata ka jingong u briew U Blei, kaba u la pyrta ïa kata ka duwan ha Bethel, u Jeroboam u la kner ïa la ka kti na ka duwan, u da ong, “Kem ïa u.” Te ka kti jong u, kaba u la kner ïa u, ka la tyrkhong, haduh ba um lah shuh ban pynran pat ïa ka sha lade.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ïa ka duwan ruh la pynkad, bad la pyntheh noh ïa ka dpei na kata ka duwan, katba kum kata ka dak kaba u briew U Blei u la lah ai da ka ktien U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u syiem u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha uta u briew U Blei, “To kyrpad mynta ïa ka jingisynei U Trai U Blei jong me, bad to duwai na ka bynta jong nga, ba yn pynbha pat ïa ka kti jong nga.” Te uta u briew U Blei u la kyrpad ïa U Trai, bad ïa ka kti u syiem la pynbha pat, bad ka la long kumba mynshuwa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha uta u briew U Blei, “Ale sha ïing bad nga, bad to da bam da dih, bad ngan ai jingai sngewbha ha me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te uta u briew U Blei u la ong ha u syiem, “Lada men ai ha nga marshiteng ka ïing jong me, ngan ym leit bsut bad me, lymne ngan ym bam kpu lymne dih um ha kane ka jaka:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> naba la hukum ïa nga kumta da ka ktien U Trai, ka da ong, ‘Men ym bam kpu lymne dih um, lymne leit phai noh da ka lynti kaba me la wan.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u la leit da kawei pat ka lynti, bad um leit phai da kata ka lynti kaba u la wan sha Bethel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la shong ha Bethel uwei u nongïathuhlypa tymmen; bad uwei na ki khun jong u, u la wan ïathuh ha u ïa ki kam baroh ba uta u briew U Blei u la leh ha kata ka sngi ha Bethel: kita ki ktien kiba u la kren ha u syiem, ïa kita ruh ki la ïathuh ha u kpa jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u kpa jong ki u la ong ha ki, “Da kano ka lynti u la leit?” Ki khun jong u te ki la ïohi da kano ka lynti ba uta u briew U Blei u la leit, uba la wan na Judah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u la ong ha la ki khun, “To teh jin ka kadda ïa nga.” Kumta, ki la teh jin ka kadda ïa u: bad u la shong halor jong ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la bud ïa uta u briew U Blei, bad u la shem ïa u ba u shong hapoh u dieng Sning: bad u la ong ha u, “Ma me mo uta u briew U Blei uba la wan na Judah?” U te u la ong, “Ma nga keiñ.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Ale sha ïing bad nga, bad bam kpu.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U te u la ong, “Ngam lah ban leit phai bad me, lymne bsut bad me: bad ngan ym bam kpu lymne dih um bad me ha kane ka jaka:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> naba la ong ha nga da ka ktien U Trai, ‘Men ym bam kpu lymne dih um hangta, lymne leit phai pat da kata ka lynti kaba me la wan.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Nga ruh nga long u nongïathuhlypa kumjuh kum me: bad u angel u la kren ha nga da ka ktien U Trai, u da ong, ‘To wallam ïa u pat bad me sha la ïing, ba un ïoh bam kpu bad dih um.’ ” Hynrei, u la lamler ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, u la leit phai pat bad u, bad u la bam kpu ha ka ïing jong u, bad u la dih um de.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad katba ki ïashong bam ha ka miej, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha uta u nongïathuhlypa uba la wallam pat ïa u:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> te u la pyrta ha uta u briew U Blei uba la wan na Judah, u da ong, “Kumne u ong U Trai, ‘Namar ba mem kohnguh ïa ka shyntur U Trai, bad mem shym la sumar ïa ka hukum kaba U Trai U Blei jong me u la hukum ïa me, hynrei, me la wan phai pat,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad me la bam kpu bad dih um ha ka jaka, ïa kaba u la ong ha me, “Wat bam kpu, lymne dih um”; ka metïap jong me kan ym phai sha ka jingtep ki kpa jong me.’ ”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ynda u la bam kpu, bad ynda u la dih um, u la teh jin ka kadda ïa u, ïa uta u nongïathuhlypa ïa uba u la pynphai pat keiñ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ynda u la leit, u sing u la ïakynduh bad u ha lynti, bad u la pynïap ïa u: bad ïa ka metïap jong u la bred ha lynti, bad ka kadda ka ïeng hajan jong ka; u sing ruh u ïeng hajan kata ka metïap.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha khmih, ki briew ki la ïaid nangta, bad ki la ïohi ïa ka metïap ba la bred ha lynti, bad ïa uta u sing ba u ïeng hajan ka metïap: bad ki la wan ïathuh ha ka shnong ha kaba la shong uta u nongïathuhlypa tymmen.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba uta u nongïathuhlypa uba la pynphai pat ïa u na kata ka lynti u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la ong, “Dei u briew U Blei, u bym shym la kohnguh ïa ka shyntur U Trai: namar kata, U Trai u la aiti ïa u ha uta u sing, uba la tar ïa u, bad u la pynïap ïa u kat kum ka ktien U Trai kaba u la kren ha u.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la kren ha la ki khun, u da ong, “To teh jin ka kadda ïa nga.” Bad ki la teh ïa ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba u la leit u la shem ïa ka metïap jong u, ba la bred ha lynti, bad ka kadda bad u sing ki ïaïeng hajan kata ka metïap: uta u sing um shym la bam ïa ka metïap, lymne tar ïa ka kadda.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad uta u nongïathuhlypa u la shim ïa ka metïap uta u briew U Blei, bad u la buh ïa ka halor ka kadda, bad u la wallam pat ïa ka: bad u la wan sha shnong jong uta u nongïathuhlypa tymmen, ban ïambriew, bad ban tep ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u la buh ïa ka metïap jong u ha ka jingtep jong u hi; bad ki la ïaïambriew ïa u, ki ïa-ong, “A ko para jong nga!”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ynda u la tep ïa u, u la kren ha la ki khun, u da ong, “Ynda nga ïap, te to tep ïa nga ha ka jingtep ha kaba la tep ïa u briew U Blei, buh ki shyieng jong nga ha syndah ki shyieng jong u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Naba kata ka jingong kaba u la pyrta da ka ktien U Trai pyrshah ïa ka duwan ha Bethel, bad pyrshah ïa ki ïing ki jaka bajrong baroh kiba don ha ki shnong ka Samaria, da shisha kan jia.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hadien kane, u Jeroboam um shym phai na ka lynti basniew jong u, hynrei, u la thung pat ki lyngdoh ki jaka bajrong napdeng u paidbah baroh: uno uno uba treh u la pynkyntang ïa u, khnang ban dup ïoh lyngdoh ïa ki jaka bajrong.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kane ka la wan long ka pop ïa ka ïing u Jeroboam, kat haduh ban pynduh noh ïa ka, bad ban pynjot noh khoit ïa ka na khmat ka khyndew."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kata ka por u Abijah u khun u Jeroboam u la pang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Jeroboam u la ong ha la ka tnga, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to ïeng, bad to pynkylla dur ïa lade, ba kin ym ithuh ba pha long ka tnga u Jeroboam; bad to leit sha Sheiloh; ha khmih, hangta don u Ahijah u nongïathuhlypa, uba la kren shaphang jong nga ba ngan long syiem halor une u paidbah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad to rah bad pha shiphew tylli ki kpu, bad ki 'putharo, bad shi klong ka ngap, bad leit ha u: un sa ïathuh ha pha aïu kan jia ïa u khynnah.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka tnga u Jeroboam ka la leh kumta bad haba ka la ïeng, ka la leit sha Sheiloh, bad ka la poi ha ïing u Ahijah. Te u Ahijah um lah ban ïohi; namar ki khmat jong u ki la byrïe namar ba u la tymmen.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Ahijah, “Ha khmih, ka tnga u Jeroboam ka wan ïakylli ïa me shaphang u khun jong ka; naba u pang: ‘kumne bad kumne men ong ha ka’: naba, haba kan wan rung hapoh, kan leh mynleh ïa lade kum kawei pat ka kynthei.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Ahijah u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa ki kjat jong ka, katba ka rung ha ka jingkhang, u la ong, “To rung, pha ka tnga u Jeroboam; balei pha leh mynleh ïa lade kum kawei pat? namar la phah ïa nga ha pha da ki khubor bajur.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Khie leit ïathuh ha u Jeroboam, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel: Namar kumba nga la kyntiew ïa me napdeng u paidbah, bad la pynlong syiem ïa me halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad nga la kad noh ïa ka hima na ka ïing u Dabid, bad nga la ai ïa ka ha me: hynrei, pynban, mem shym la long kum u shakri jong nga u Dabid, uba la sumar ïa ki hukum jong nga, bad uba la bud ïa nga da ka dohnud jong u baroh, ban leh tang kata kaba dei ha khmat jong nga;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hynrei, me la leh ka basniew tam ïa kita baroh kiba la long ha shuwa jong me, bad me la leit thaw ïa lade kiwei pat ki blei, bad ki dur bleithaw ba la saiñ, ban pankwah ïa nga ban bitar, bad me la bred ïa nga shadien jong me:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> namar kata, ha khmih, ngan wallam ka basniew halor ka ïing u Jeroboam, bad ngan ot noh na u Jeroboam u khun shynrang baroh, ïa uta uba la ker tawiar, bad ïa uta uba laitluid ha Israel, bad ngan sar lut ïa ka ïing u Jeroboam, kumba u briew u sar noh ïa ka jakhlia, haduh ban da lut phar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ïa uta uba ïap na ki jong u Jeroboam hapoh shnong, ki ksew kin bam; bad ïa uta uba ïap ha lum, kin bam ki sim bneng: naba U Trai u la kren ïa kata.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To ïeng joit pha namar kata, khie leit sha la ïing: te haba ki kjat jong pha ki jam hapoh shnong, uta u khynnah un ïap.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad baroh ki Israel kin ïaïambriew na ka bynta jong u, bad kin tep ïa u; namar tang ma u hi na ki jong u Jeroboam un poi sha ka jingtep: namar ha u la shem katto katne ka babha sha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ha ka ïing u Jeroboam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nalor kata, U Trai ruh un pynmih ïa u syiem halor ki Israel, u ban pynduh noh ïa ka ïing u Jeroboam ha kata ka sngi: te kumno pat? mynta keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba U Trai un shoh ïa ki Israel, kumba la pynkhih ïa u khah ha um; bad un rat noh ïa ki Israel na kane ka ri ka babha, kaba u la ai ha ki kpa jong ki, bad un pynsakma ïa ki sha lyndet ka Wah; naba ki la thaw ïa ki Asherim jong ki, ki da pankwah ïa U Trai ban bitar.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te un sa iehnoh noh ïa ki Israel namar ki pop u Jeroboam, uba la leh pop, bad da ki u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka tnga u Jeroboam haba ka la ïeng joit, ka la leit noh, bad ka la poi sha Tirsah: te hamar ba ka la poi ha ka jingkhang ka ïing, uta u khynnah u la ïap.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad baroh ki Israel ki la tep ïa u, bad ki la ïambriew na ka bynta jong u; katba kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren da ka kti u shakri jong u, u Ahijah u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kita kiwei ki jingleh u Jeroboam, kumno u la ïaleh thma, bad kumno u la synshar, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki sngi kiba u Jeroboam u la synshar ki la long arphew ar snem: bad u la thiah bad ki kpa jong u, bad u Nadab u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon u la synshar ha Judah. U Rehoboam u la long sawphew wei snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar khathynñiew snem ha Jerusalem; ka nongbah kaba U Trai u la jied na ki jaid Israel baroh, ban buh ïa la ka kyrteng hangta: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Naamah” ka nong Ammon.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki Judah ki la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai; bad ki la pynskuiñ ïa u da ki pop jong ki kiba ki la leh, nalor kita baroh ba ki kpa jong ki, ki la leh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar ki la tei ruh ha ki, ïa ki jaka bajrong, bad ki mawbynna, bad ki Asherim, halor u lum bajrong baroh, bad hapoh ka dieng bajyrngam baroh;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad la don ruh ki kynja Sodom ha ka ri: ki la leh katba kum kita ki jingijli baroh jong ki jaid bynriew kiba U Trai u la beh noh ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha ka snem ka basan u syiem Rehoboam, u Shishak u syiem ka Ijipt u la wan kiew pyrshah ïa ka Jerusalem:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad u la shim ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem; u la shim noh baroh keiñ: bad u la shim de ïa kita ki stieh ksiar baroh kiba u Solomon u la thaw.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U syiem Rehoboam te u la thaw pli ha ki jaka jong ki da ki stieh rnong, bad u la aiti ïa ki ha ki kti ki kaptan jong ki santari kiba ap ïa ka jingkhang ka ïing u syiem.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te borabor katba u syiem u leit sha ka ïing U Trai, ki santari ki bah ïa ki, bad ki wallam pat ïa ki sha ka kamra ki santari.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Rehoboam, bad baroh kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad la don ka thma hapdeng u Rehoboam bad u Jeroboam borabor.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Rehoboam u la thiah noh bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u lem bad ki kpa jong u ha ka nongbah u Dabid: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Naamah” ka nong Ammon. Bad u Abijam u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka snem ka bakhatphra u syiem Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, u Abijam u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Judah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Lai snem u la synshar ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Maakah” ka khun u Abishalom.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ki pop u kpa jong u baroh, kiba u la leh mynshuwa jong u: ka dohnud jong u te kam shym long janai bad U Trai U Blei jong u, kum ka dohnud u kpa jong u, u Dabid.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> La kumta ruh, na ka bynta u Dabid, U Trai U Blei jong u, U la ai ïa u ka sharak ha Jerusalem, ïa ka ban pynïeng ïa u khun jong u hadien jong u, bad ban pynskhem ïa ka Jerusalem:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> namar u Dabid u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha ki khmat U Trai, bad um shym la phai noh na kaei kaei kaba U la hukum ïa u baroh ki sngi ka rta ka jingim jong u, lait sa ka kam u Uriah u nong Hit.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te la don ka thma hapdeng u Rehoboam bad u Jeroboam baroh ki sngi ka rta jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Abijam bad baroh kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah? Bad la don ka thma hapdeng u Abijam bad u Jeroboam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Abijam u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u; bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka nongbah u Dabid: te u Asa u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ha ka snem ka ba-arphew u Jeroboam u syiem ki Israel, u Asa u la sdang ban synshar halor ka Judah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la synshar sawphew wei snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u “ka Maakah” ka khun u Abishalom.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Asa u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha ki khmat U Trai, kumba la leh u Dabid u kpa jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la beh noh ïa ki kynja Sodom na ka ri, bad u la pynduh noh ïa ki bleithaw baroh ïa kiba ki kpa jong u ki la thaw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ïa ka Maakah ruh ka kmie jong u, u la pynduh noh na ka ban long syiem, namar ka la thaw ka dur ba-ijli ïa ki Asherah; bad u Asa u la pom noh ïa ka dur jong ki, bad u la thang ïa ka hajan ka wah Kidron.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki jaka bajrong ym shym la pynduh noh: la kumta ruh ka dohnud u Asa ka la janai ha U Trai baroh ki sngi jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la wallam ha ïing U Trai ïa kita kiei kiei ba u kpa jong u, u la pynkyntang, bad ïa kita kiei kiei kiba u hi u la pynkyntang, ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, bad ki kynja pliang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te la don ka thma hapdeng u Asa bad u Baasha u syiem ki Israel baroh ki sngi jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Baasha u syiem ki Israel u la leit kiew pyrshah ïa ka Judah, bad u la tei ïa ka Ramah, ba un ym shah ïano ïano ban ïaleit ïawan sha u Asa u syiem ka Judah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u Asa u la shim ïa ka rupa bad ka ksiar baroh kiba dang don ha ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem, bad u la aiti ïa ki ha ka kti ki shakri jong u: bad u la phah ïa ki sha u Benhadad, u khun u Tabrimmon, u khun u Hesion, u syiem ka Syria, uba shong ha Damaskos, u da ong,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Don ka jingïateh lok hapdeng jong nga bad jong me, hapdeng u kpa jong nga bad u kpa jong me: ha khmih, nga la phah ha me ka jingnguh da ka rupa bad ka ksiar; to khie leit, ïa-pynduh noh ïa ka jingïateh lok jong me bad u Baasha u syiem ki Israel, ba un dup leit noh na nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta u Benhadad u la sngew ïa u Asa u syiem, bad u la phah ïa ki kaptan ki paidïapom jong u pyrshah ïa ki nongbah ki Israel, bad u la jop ïa ka Ijon, bad ka Dan bad ka Abel-beth-maakah, bad ka Khinneroth baroh, lem bad ka ri Naphtali baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ynda u Baasha u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la keiñ noh kaba tei ïa ka Ramah, bad u la shong ha Tirsah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Asa u la pynbna ha ki Judah baroh; uwei ruh um lait: bad ki la kit noh ïa ki maw jong ka Ramah, bad ïa ki dieng jong ka, da kiba u Baasha u la tei; bad u syiem Asa u la tei da ki ïa ka Geba Benjamin, bad ka Mispah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Asa baroh, bad ka bor jong u baroh, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ïa ki nongbah kiba u la tei, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah? Hynrei, ha ka por ba u la tymmen u la pang na ki kjat jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Asa u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u bad ki kpa jong u ha ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u: bad u Jehoshaphat u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Nadab u khun u Jeroboam u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha ka snem ka ba-ar jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, bad u la synshar halor ki Israel ar snem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti u kpa jong u, bad ha ka pop jong u da kaba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Baasha u khun u Ahijah, na ka ïing u Issakhar, u la ïashet pyrshah ïa u; bad u Baasha u la pom ïa u ha Gibbethon, kaba dei ïa ki Philistia; namar u Nadab bad baroh ki Israel ki dang ïaker kut ïa ka Gibbethon.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ha ka snem ka balai jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Baasha u la pynïap ïa u, bad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u tang shu la long syiem, u la pom lut ïa ka ïing u Jeroboam baroh, um shym la pynsah ïa u Jeroboam uwei ruh em, haduh ba u la pynduh noh khoit ïa u; katba kum ka jingong U Trai, kaba u la kren da u shakri jong u, u Ahijah u nong Shilon:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na ka bynta ki pop u Jeroboam kiba u la leh pop, bad da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel; namar ka jingpankwah jong u da kaba u la pankwah ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel ban bitar.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Nadab, bad baroh kiba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te la don ka thma hapdeng u Asa bad u Baasha u syiem ki Israel baroh ki sngi jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ha ka snem ka balai jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Baasha u khun u Ahijah u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel baroh ha Tirsah, bad u la synshar arphew saw snem.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, u la ïaid ruh ha ka lynti u Jeroboam, bad ha ka pop jong u da kaba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Jehu u khun u Hanani pyrshah ïa u Baasha, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Namar kumba nga la kyntiew ïa me na ka 'dewmet, bad la pynlong syiem ïa me halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel; bad me la ïaid ha ka lynti u Jeroboam, bad me la pynleh pop ïa ki briew jong nga ki Israel, ban pankwah ïa nga ban bitar da ki pop jong ki;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ha khmih, ngan sar noh khoit ïa u Baasha bad ïa ka ïing jong u; bad ngan pynlong ïa ka ïing jong me kum ka ïing u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ïa uta uba ïap na ki jong u Baasha ha ka nongbah, ki ksew kin bam; bad ïa uta uba ïap na ki jong u sha lum, ki sim bneng kin bam.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Baasha, bad kaba u la leh, bad ka bor jong u, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Baasha te u la thiah noh lem bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u ha Tirsah; bad u Elah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te nalor kata da ka kti u Jehu u nongïathuhlypa u khun u Hanani, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan pyrshah ïa u Baasha, bad pyrshah ïa ka ïing jong u, kawei namar kata ka basniew baroh kaba u la leh ha khmat U Trai, ban pankwah ïa u ban bitar bad ka kam ki kti jong u, ba u long kum ka ïing u Jeroboam, bad kawei pat namar ba u la pynïap ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha ka snem ka ba-arphew hynriew jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Elah u khun u Baasha u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Tirsah, bad u la synshar ar snem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Simri u shakri jong u, u kaptan shiteng ki kali ïapom jong u, u la shet pyrshah ïa u: ha kane u don ha Tirsah, u da dih pynbuaid ïa lade ha ïing u Arsa, uba halor ka ïing ha Tirsah:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u Simri u la rung shapoh bad u la pom ïa u, bad u la pynïap ïa u, ha ka snem arphew hynñiew jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, bad u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda u la sdang ban synshar, u tang shu la shong halor ka khet jong u, u la pynïap ïa ka ïing u Baasha baroh: um shym la pynsah ïa u wat uwei u khun shynrang, lymne na ki kur jong u, lymne na ki lok jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumne u Simri u la pynduh noh khoit ïa ka ïing u Baasha, katba kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren pyrshah ïa u Baasha da u Jehu u nongïathuhlypa,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> namar ki pop u Baasha baroh, bad ki pop u Elah u khun jong u, kiba ki la leh pop, bad da kiba ki la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel, ban pankwah ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ban bitar da ki jingthala jong ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Elah, bad baroh kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ha ka snem arphew hynñiew jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Simri u la synshar hynñiew sngi ha Tirsah. Te u paidbah u la dang shong dara ban shong ïaleh ïa ka Gibbethon, kaba dei ïa ki Philistia.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad uta u paidbah uba dang shong dara u la bna ba ki ong, “U Simri u la shet pyrshah, bad u la pynïap ruh ïa u syiem:” namar kata, ki Israel baroh ki la thung ïa u Omri, u kaptan u paidïapom, ban long u syiem halor ki Israel ha kata ka sngi ha ka dara.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Omri u la leit kiew na Gibbethon, bad ki Israel lem bad u, bad ki la ker kut ïa ka Tirsah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba u Simri u la ïohi ba la jop ïa ka shnong, u la leit rung shapoh ka kut ka ïing u syiem, bad u la thang ïa ka ïing u syiem halor jong u da ka ding, bad u la ïap,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> namar ki pop kiba u la leh pop ha kaba leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, ha kaba ïaid ha ka lynti u Jeroboam, bad ha ka pop jong u kaba u la leh, ban pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Simri, bad ka jingshet pyrshah jong u kaba u la leh, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta te, u paidbah Israel u la pait ar liang: shi bynta na u paidbah ki la bud ïa u Tibni u khun u Ginath, ban thung syiem ïa u; bad shiteng ki la bud ïa u Omri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u paidbah uba bud ïa u Omri u la lah ïa u paidbah uba bud ïa u Tibni u khun u Ginath: kumta u Tibni u la ïap, bad u Omri u la synshar.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha ka snem laiphew wei jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Omri u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel, bad u la synshar khat-ar snem: hynriew snem u la synshar ha Tirsah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u la thied ar talent rupa ïa u lum rit Samaria na u Shemer; bad u la tei halor uta u lum, bad u la kyrteng ïa ka shnong kaba u la tei, katba kum ka kyrteng u Shemer, u trai uta u lum Samaria.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Omri u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad u la leh bymman palat ïa kita baroh kiba la mynshuwa jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba u la ïaid ha baroh ka lynti u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, bad ha ki pop jong u da kiba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel, ban pankwah ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ban bitar da ki jingthala jong ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te kiwei ki jingleh u Omri kiba u la leh, bad ka bor kaba u la pyni, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Omri u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u ha Samaria: bad u Ahab u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ha ka balaiphew phra snem jong u Asa u syiem ka Judah, u Ahab u khun u Omri u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel: bad u Ahab u khun u Omri u la synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria arphew ar snem.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Ahab u khun u Omri u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai palat ïa kita baroh kiba la mynshuwa jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te kumba ka la long pynban ka kam kaba sting ïa u ban ïaid ha ki pop u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, u la shongkurim ïa ka Jesebel ka khun u Ethbaal u syiem ki nong Sidon, bad u la leit shakri ïa u Baal, bad u la mane ïa u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U la tei duwan ruh ïa u Baal ha ka ïing u Baal, kaba u la tei ha Samaria.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Ahab u la thaw ïa ki Asherah: bad u Ahab u la leh kham bun ban pankwah ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ban bitar pynban ban ïa ki syiem ki Israel baroh kiba la mynshuwa jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ha ki sngi jong u, u Hiel u nong Bethel u la tei ïa ka Jerikho: haba u pynshong nongrim ïa ka, u la duh noh ïa u Abiram u khun nyngkong jong u, bad haba u la pynïeng ïa ki khyrdop jong ka, u la duh noh ïa u khun khatduh jong u, u Segub, katba kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren da ka kti u Joshua u khun u Nun."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Elijah u nong Tishbi, uba la long uwei na ki nong Gilead, u la ong ha u Ahab, “Katba im U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ha khmat jong uba nga ïeng, kan ym don umjer lymne slap ha kine ki snem, hynrei, tang katba kum ka ktien jong nga.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u, ka da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “To mih me nangne, bad leit shaphang mihngi, bad buhrieh ïa lade hajan ka wah Kherith, kaba long ha khmat ka Jordan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad men dih na kata ka wah; bad nga la hukum ïa ki tyngab ban bsa ïa me hangta.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u la leit bad u la leh kat kum ka ktien U Trai; naba u la leit shong hajan ka wah Kherith, kaba ha khmat ka Jordan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki tyngab te ki la wallam kpu bad doh mynstep, bad kpu bad doh la janmiet; bad u la dih na kata ka wah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te hadien katto katne, kata ka wah ka la rngad, namar bym shym la don slap ha ka ri.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka ktien U Trai te ka la wan ha u, ka da ong,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “To ïeng joit, khie leit sha Sarephat, kaba dei ïa ka Sidon, bad shong hangta: ha khmih, nga la hukum ïa ka riewkynthei kaba hangta ban bsa ïa me.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u la ïeng bad u la leit sha Sarephat; te haba u la poi sha ka khyrdop ka shnong, ha khmih, ka riewkynthei ka la don hangta kaba lum dieng prew; te ynda u la khot ïa ka, u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to wallam ïa nga khyndiat ka um ha ka khuri, ba ngan ïoh dih.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ka dang leit ban wallam ïa ka, u la khot ïa ka, u la ong ruh, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to wallam kpu ïa nga khyndiat ha ka kti jong pha.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “Katba im U Trai U Blei jong me, ngam don uwei u kpu, hynrei, tang shi kham u 'purew ha ka shang, bad khyndiat ka umphniang ha u klong: bad ha khmih, nga shu khar ar tylli ki dieng prew, ba ngan ïoh leit sha ïing bad shet ïa ka, ïa lade bad ïa u khun jong nga, ba ngin bam ïa ka, bad ïap noh.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Elijah u la ong ha ka, “Wat sheptieng; to leit bad leh kumba pha la ong: hynrei, to khreh shuwa ïa nga iwei i kpu barit, bad wallam ïa ita sha nga, bad hadien kata, sa khreh ïa lade bad ïa u khun jong pha.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u 'purew ha kata ka shang un ym lut, lymne ka umphniang ha uta u klong kan ym duh, tad ynda kata ka sngi ba U Trai un phah slap ha ka khyndew.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka te ka la leit bad ka la leh kat kum ka jingong u Elijah: bad ma ka, bad ma u, bad ka ïing jong ka, ki la ïabam bun sngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U 'purew ha kata ka shang um shym la lut, lymne ka umphniang ha uta u klong kam shym la duh, katba kum ka ktien U Trai, kaba u la kren da u Elijah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei, u khun kata ka kynthei, ka trai kata ka ïing, u la pang; te ka jingpang ka la jur katta katta, katba kam sah mynsiem shuh ha u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka la ong ha u Elijah, “Nga dei aïu ïa me, A me u briew U Blei? pleng me la wan ha nga ban pynkynmaw ïa ka pop jong nga, bad ban pynïap ïa u khun jong nga!”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U te u la ong ha ka, “To ai ha nga ïa u khun jong pha.” Bad u la shim ïa u na ka shadem jong ka, bad u la leit rah ïa u sha ka kamra, ha kaba u ju shong, bad u la buh ïa u ha ka jingthiah jong u hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la kyrpad jam ha U Trai, bad u la ong, “A Trai U Blei jong nga, me la wallam ruh ïa ka basniew ha kane ka riewkynthei bad kaba nga shong, da kaba pynïap ïa u khun jong ka?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la dem ïa lade halor uta u khynnah lai sien, bad u la kyrpad jam ha U Trai, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, A Trai U Blei jong nga, to shah ba ka mynsiem une u khynnah kan wan pat ha u.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad U Trai u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien u Elijah; bad ka mynsiem uta u khynnah ka la wan pat ha u, bad u la im pat.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Elijah u la shim ïa uta u khynnah, bad u la wallam ïa u na ka kamra sha ïing, bad u la aiti ïa u ha ka kmie jong u: bad u Elijah u la ong, “Ha khmih, u khun jong pha u im.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kata ka kynthei te ka la ong ha u Elijah, “Mynta nga tip ba me long u briew U Blei, bad ba ka ktien U Trai ha ka shyntur jong me ka long kaba shisha.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien bun sngi, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Elijah, ha ka snem ka balai, kaba ong, “Khie leit, pyni ïa lade ha u Ahab; ynda kumta te, ngan sa phah slap ha ka khyndew.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Elijah u la leit pyni ïa lade ha u Ahab. Te ka 'nemsniew ka la jur eh ha Samaria.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Ahab u la khot ïa u Obadaïah, uba halor ka ïing. (Te une u Obadaïah u la sheptieng ïa U Trai shikatdei:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> naba mynba ka Jesebel ka la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa U Trai, u Obadaïah u la shim shispah ngut ki nongïathuhlypa, bad u la buhrieh ïa ki sanphew sanphew ha ka krem, bad u la bsa ïa ki da u kpu bad da ka um.)",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Ahab u la ong ïa u Obadaïah, “Khie leit lyngba ka ri, sha ki umpohliew baroh, bad sha ki wah baroh: lehse ngi lah ban shem phlang bad ri im ïa ki kulai bad ki khashor, ba ngin ym duh noh ïa ki mrad baroh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, ki la ïabynta ïa ka ri hapdeng jong ki ban ïaid lyngba ïa ka: u Ahab u la leit da lade hi na kawei ka lynti, bad u Obadaïah u la leit da lade hi na kawei pat ka lynti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te katba u Obadaïah u dang ha lynti, ha khmih, u Elijah u la ïakynduh ïa u: bad u la ithuh ïa u, bad u la dem ngon la ka khmat, u ong ruh, “Wa dei ma me pleng, ko kynrad, u Elijah?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U te u la ïathuh ïa u, “Nga dei keiñ: to leit, ïathuh ïa u kynrad jong me, ‘Ha khmih, u Elijah u don hangne.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U te u la ong, “Ha kaei nga la leh pop, ba men ai noh ïa la u shakri ha ka kti u Ahab, ban pynïap ïa nga?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Katba im U Trai U Blei jong me, ym don ka jaid bynriew lane ka hima, sha kaba u kynrad jong nga um shym la phah ban wad ïa me: bad haba ki ong, ‘Um don hangne’, u pynsmai ïa kata ka hima bad kata ka jaid bynriew, ba kim shym la shem ïa me.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te me ong pynban, ‘To leit, ïathuh ïa u kynrad jong me, Ha khmih, u Elijah u don hangne.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te nga tang shu leit noh na me, U Mynsiem U Trai un rah ïa me sha kaba nga ngam tip; te kumta ynda nga wan ïathuh ha u Ahab, bad um lah ban shem ïa me, un pynïap ïa nga: hynrei ma nga, u shakri jong me, nga sheptieng ïa U Trai la myndang khynnah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ym shym la ïathuh ïa u kynrad jong nga ïa kaei ba nga la leh, mynba ka Jesebel ka la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa U Trai, kumno ba nga la buhrieh shispah ngut na ki nongïathuhlypa U Trai sanphew sanphew ha ka krem, bad nga la bsa ïa ki da u kpu bad da ka um?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te mynta me ong, ‘To leit ïathuh ha u kynrad, Ha khmih, u Elijah u don hangne’: bad un pynïap ïa nga.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Elijah te u la ong, “Katba im U Trai ki paid, ha khmat jong uba nga ïeng, da shisha ngan pyni ïa lade ha u ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Obadaïah u la leit shem ïa u Ahab, bad u la ïathuh ïa u: bad u Ahab u la leit shem ïa u Elijah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ynda u Ahab u la ïohi ïa u Elijah, u Ahab u la ong ïa u, “Long ma me, me u nongpynshitom ki Israel?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Nga ngam shym pynshitom ïa ki Israel; hynrei, ma me keiñ, bad ka ïing u kpa jong me, ha kaba phi la lyndet ïa ki hukum U Trai, bad ba me la leit bud ïa ki Baal.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te namar kata, to phah ïalum lang ha nga ïa ki Israel baroh ha u lum Karmel, bad ïa ki nongïathuhlypa u Baal sawspah sanphew, bad ïa ki nongïathuhlypa ki Asherah sawspah ngut kiba bam ja ha ka miej ka Jesebel.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta u Ahab u la phah ha ki khun Israel baroh, bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki nongïathuhlypa ha u lum Karmel.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u Elijah u la wan hajan uta u paidbah baroh, u la ong, “Sa katno pat phin ïeng lyngngoh hapdeng ar ki jingmut? lada U Trai u long U Blei, to bud ïa u: hynrei, lada u Baal, te to bud ïa uta.” U paidbah te um shym jubab ïa u shikyntien ruh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta te, u Elijah u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Ma nga, tang marwei hi, nga dang sah u nongïathuhlypa jong U Trai, hynrei, ki nongïathuhlypa u Baal ki long sawspah sanphew ngut.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata, to kin ai ïa ngi ar tylli ki masi dab; bad to kin jied uwei u masi dab ïa ki, bad to kin ot tukra ïa u, bad kin buh ïa u halor ki dieng, te kin ym buh ding hapoh: nga ruh ngan khreh ïa uta uwei u masi dab, bad ngan buh ïa u halor ki dieng, bad ngan ym buh ding hapoh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad to khot ma phi ha ka kyrteng uta u blei jong phi, nga ruh ngan khot ha ka kyrteng jong U Trai: te uta U Blei uba phah da ka ding, to un long U Blei.” Bad uta u paidbah baroh u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Kata ka ktien kaba dei.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Elijah u la ong ha ki nongïathuhlypa u Baal, “To jied shuwa ma phi ïa uwei u masi, bad to khreh ïa u; naba phi long shibun; bad to khot ha ka kyrteng u blei jong phi, hynrei, wat buh ding hapoh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki la shim ïa uta u masi dab uba la ai ha ki, bad ki la khreh ïa u, bad ki la khot ha ka kyrteng u Baal naduh mynstep jin haduh shiteng sngi, ki ïa-ong, “A Baal, to sngew ïa ngi.” Hynrei, ym shym don ktien ei ei, lymne uno uno ba jubab. Bad ki la ïarynsied sawdong kata ka duwan kaba la thaw.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te hamar shiteng sngi, u Elijah u la kren mynthi ïa ki, bad u la ong, “Da pyrta jam: naba u long blei; haba lehse u dang pyrkhat, lane u dang mih shabar, lane u dang leit jingleit, lane lehse u thiah kai, bad ka dei ban kyrsiew ïa u.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki la ïapyrta jam, bad ki la ot ïa lade kat kum ka rukom jong ki da ki tari bad da ki wait sum, ha ban da la mih ka snam halor jong ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba la palat shiteng sngi ruh, ki la ïathuhlypa haduh ka por ainguh ïa ka jingkñia la janmiet; hynrei, ym shym la don ktien ei ei, lymne uno uno ba jubab, lymne uno uno ba suidñiew.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Elijah u la ong ha uta u paidbah baroh, “To wan hajan jong nga;” u paidbah baroh te u la wan hajan jong u. Bad u la shna ïa ka duwan U Trai ïa kaba la pyntwa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Elijah u la shim khat-ar tylli ki maw, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki jaid ki khun u Jakob, ha uba ka ktien U Trai ka la wan, ka da ong, “ ‘U Israel’ kan long ka kyrteng jong me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Da kita ki maw te u la tei ka duwan ha ka kyrteng U Trai; bad u la tih kharai sawdong ïa ka duwan, kat ban ngiam ar byrni u symbai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la buh ter ter ïa ki dieng bad u la ot tukra ïa uta u masi dab, bad u la buh ïa u halor kita ki dieng. Te u la ong, “To pyndap saw tylli ki pipa da ka um, bad theh ïa ka halor ka jingainguh thang, bad halor ki dieng.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la ong, “Leh kumjuh sa shi sien; te ki la leh sa shi sien.” Bad u la ong, “Leh kumjuh sa shi sien pat;” te ki la leh pat sa shi sien.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad kata ka um ka la tuid sawdong ïa ka duwan; bad u la pyndap ïa ka kharai ruh da ka um.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te hamar ka por ainguh ïa ka jingkñia la janmiet, u Elijah u nongïathuhlypa u la wan hajan, bad u la ong, “A Trai, U Blei jong u Abraham, u jong u Isaak, bad u jong u Israel, to pyntip ha kane ka sngi ba me long U Blei ha Israel, bad ba nga long ma nga u shakri jong me, bad ba nga la leh ïa kine kiei kiei baroh da ka ktien jong me.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sngew ïa nga, A Trai, to sngew ïa nga, ba une u paidbah un ïoh tip ba ma me, U Trai, me long U Blei, bad ba me la pynphai pat ïa ka dohnud jong ki.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ynda kumta, ka ding na U Trai ka la hap, bad ka la bam duh ïa kata ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa kita ki dieng, bad ïa kita ki maw, bad ïa ka dpei, bad ka la kjit noh ïa kata ka um kaba ha kata ka kharai.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba uta u paidbah baroh u la ïohi ïa kata, ki la dem ngon la ki khmat; bad ki la ong, “U Trai, uta u long U Blei; U Trai, uta u long U Blei.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u Elijah u la ong ha ki, “Kem ïa ki nongïathuhlypa u Baal; wat ai ban lait uwei ruh na ki.” Bad ki la kem ïa ki: bad u Elijah u la leit lam ïa ki arsut sha ka wah Kishon, bad u la pynïap ïa ki hangta.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Elijah u la ong ha u Ahab, “To ïeng joit, leit bam leit dih; namar don ka jingkyrhuh slap shikatdei.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kumta u Ahab u leit kiew ban bam ban dih. U Elijah ruh u la leit kiew sha khlieh u lum Karmel; bad u la dem ïa lade ha khyndew bad u la buh ïa la ka khmat hapdeng ki khohsiew jong u.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u la ong ha la u shakri, “To leit kiew, khmih shaphang ka duriaw.” Te haba u la leit kiew bad u la khmih, u ong, “Ym don ei ei.” U te u ong, “To leit pat hynñiew sien.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te ha ka bahynñiew sien, u ong, “Ha khmih, don u lyoh uba mih na ka duriaw, uba rit kat ka kti u briew.” U te u ong, “To khie joit, ong ha u Ahab, ‘Khreh ïa la ka kali, bad to leit hiar noh, ba u slap un ym khang ïa me.’ ”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te sa tang katto katne, ka bneng ka la ïong namar ki lyoh bad ka lyer, bad la hap u 'lap bah. Te u Ahab u la shong kali, bad u la leit sha Jesril.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ka kti U Trai te ka la don ha u Elijah; bad haba u la panpoh la ka syngkai, u la phet sha shuwa u Ahab haduh ban da poi sha Jesril."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Ahab u la ïathuh ïa ka Jesebel ïa baroh kaba u Elijah u la leh, bad kumno ruh ba u la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa baroh da ka waitlam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Jesebel ka la phah nonglam-ktien sha u Elijah, ka da ong, “To ki blei kin leh kumta ïa nga, bad palat ruh, lada ngan ym pynlong hamar kane ka por lashai ïa ka jingim jong me kum ka jingim jong uwei na kita.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa kata, u la ïeng joit, bad u la phet noh namar la ka jingim, bad u la leit poi sha Beer-sheba, kaba dei ïa ka Judah, bad u la iehnoh ïa la u shakri hangta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u hi u la leit shi sngi lynti sha ka ri khlaw, te haba u la poi u la shong hapoh u dieng Ratam: bad u la duwai na ka bynta ïa lade ba un ïap noh; u la ong ruh, “Ka la biang katta; mynta A Trai, to shim noh ïa ka jingim jong nga; naba ngam long kham bha ban ïa ki kpa jong nga.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la thiah bad u la ïohthiah hapoh u dieng Ratam; te ha khmih, u angel u la ktah ïa u, bad u la ong ha u, “Khie joit bad to bam.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad haba u la khmih te, ha khmih, la don hajan ka khlieh jong u, u kpu ba la shet ha u rnga ding, bad shi klong ka um. Te haba u la bam la dih, u la thiah noh pat.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la wan sa shi sien bad u la ktah ïa u, u la ong ruh, “Khie joit bad to bam; namar ka jingleit ka jngai eh ïa me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba u la khie, u la bam u la dih bad u la ïaid ha ka bor kata ka jingbam sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet haduh u Horeb u lum U Blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad hangta u la leit rung sha ka krem, bad u la shong hangta; te, ha khmih, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u, bad u ong ha u, “Me leh aïu hangne, ko Elijah?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga la sngewskuiñ shikatdei na ka bynta U Trai, U Blei ki paid; naba ki khun Israel ki la lyndet ïa ka jutang jong me, ki la pynkyllon ïa ki duwan jong me, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong me da ka waitlam: bad sa tang ma nga hi nga dang sah; bad ki wad ruh ïa ka jingim jong nga, ban shim noh ïa ka.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la ong, “Mih noh, bad leit ïeng halor u lum ha khmat U Trai.” Te, ha khmih, U Trai u la ïaid nangta, bad ka 'erïong bakhraw bad bajur ka la kad ïa ki lum, bad ka la pynpait lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki mawsiang ha khmat U Trai; hynrei, U Trai um shym don ha kata ka lyer: te hadien kata ka lyer, sa kaba khynñiuh jumai; hynrei, U Trai um shym don ha kata kaba khynñiuh jumai:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> te hadien kata kaba khynñiuh jumai, sa ka ding; hynrei, U Trai um shym don ha kata ka ding: bad hadien kata ka ding, sa ka jingsawa kaba jem jai jai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u Elijah u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la tap ïa la ka khmat da la ka barandi, bad u la mih noh, bad u la ïeng ha ka shyntur kata ka krem. Te, ha khmih, ka ktien ka la wan ha u, kaba ong, “Me leh aïu hangne, ko Elijah?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga la sngewskuiñ eh na ka bynta U Trai, U Blei ki paid; naba ki khun Israel ki la lyndet noh ïa ka jutang jong me, ki la pynkyllon ïa ki duwan jong me, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong me da ka waitlam; bad sa tang ma nga hi nga dang sah; bad ki wad ruh ïa ka jingim jong nga, ban shim noh ïa ka.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u, “To khie, da leit phai pat sha ka ri khlaw ka Damaskos: te ynda me poi, men pynsleh ïa u Hasael ban long u syiem ka Syria:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ïa u Jehu u khun u Nimshi men pynsleh ban long syiem halor ki Israel; bad ïa u Elisha u khun u Shaphat na Abel-meholah men pynsleh ban long u nongïathuhlypa ha ka jaka jong me.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kan long, ba uta u ban lait na ka waitlam u Hasael, u Jehu un pynïap ïa u: bad uta u ban lait na ka waitlam u Jehu, u Elisha un pynïap ïa u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> La kumta ruh, ngan pynsah hynñiew hajar ngut ha Israel, ki khohsiew baroh ki bym shym la dem ha u Baal, bad ki shyntur baroh ki bym shym la doh ïa u.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta u la leit noh nangta, bad u la shem ïa u Elisha u khun u Shaphat, uba dang lur bad khat-ar lyngkor ki masi ha shuwa jong u, bad u hi bad kata kaba khat-ar: u Elijah te u la ïaid najan jong u, bad u la bred ïa la ka barandi halor jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba u la iehnoh ïa kita ki masi, u la phet na shadien u Elijah, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan leit doh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, te hadien kata, ngan sa bud ïa me.” U te u la ong ha u, “To leit phai pat; naba nga la leh aïu ïa me?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad haba u la phai na kaba bud ïa u, u la shim ïa kita shi jur ki masi, bad u la pynïap ïa ki, bad u la syang ïa ka doh jong ki da ki tiar kita ki masi, bad u la ai ha kita ki briew, bad ki la ïabam. Ynda kumta, u la ïeng joit, bad u la bud ïa u Elijah, bad u la shakri ïa u."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria u la ïalum lang ïa u paidïapom jong u baroh: bad la don lem bad u laiphew ar ki syiem, bad ki kulai bad ki kali: te haba u la leit kiew u la ker kut ïa ka Samaria, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la phah nonglam-ktien sha u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, shapoh shnong, bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong u Benhadad,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ‘Ka rupa jong me bad ka ksiar jong me ki long ki jong nga; ki tnga jong me ruh bad ki khun jong me, kita kiba kham bhabriew, ki long ki jong nga.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Katba kum ka jingong jong me, kynrad jong nga, A syiem; nga long u jong me, bad baroh kat kaba nga don.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kita ki nonglam-ktien te ki la wan sa shi sien, bad ki la ong, “Kumne u kren u Benhadad, u da ong, ‘Nga la phah shisha ha me, da kaba ong, “Men aiti noh ha nga ïa ka rupa jong me, bad ïa ka ksiar jong me, bad ïa ki tnga jong me, bad ïa ki khun jong me;”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hynrei, ngan phah ïa ki shakri jong nga sha me hamar kane ka por lashai, bad kin ïit ïa ka ïing jong me, bad ïa ki ïing ki shakri jong me, bad kaei kaei kaba itynnad ha ki khmat jong me, ïa kata kin shim ha la ki kti, bad kin rah noh ïa ka.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ki Israel u la khot ïa ki tymmen jong ka ri baroh, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to pyrkhat, bad to khmih kumno ba une u briew u wad ïa ka jingpynsniew: naba u la phah ha nga ban ïoh ïa ki tnga jong nga, bad ïa ki khun jong nga, bad ïa ka rupa jong nga, bad ïa ka ksiar jong nga; bad ngam shym kyrngah ïa u.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kita ki tymmen baroh bad uta u paidbah baroh ki la ong ïa u, “Wat sngap, lymne kohnguh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, u la ong ha kita ki nonglam-ktien u Benhadad, “To ïathuh ha u syiem kynrad, ‘Baroh kaba me la phah ha la u shakri ha kaba nyngkong ngan leh: hynrei, ïa kane ngam lah ban leh.’ ” Kita ki nonglam-ktien te ki la leit noh, bad ki la wallam ktien pat ha u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Benhadad u la phah ha u, bad u la ong, “To ki blei kin leh kumta ïa nga, bad tam ruh, lada ka khyndew ka Samaria kan biang mar shi kham shi kham ïa u paidbah uba bud ïa nga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la jubab bad u la ong, “To ïathuh ha u, ‘Uta uba kieng la ki atiar to un ym leh risa kum uta uba law noh ïa ki.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ynda u Benhadad u la ïohsngew ïa kane ka ktien, katba u dang dih ha kita ki ïingjaiñ, ma u bad kita ki syiem, u la ong ha la ki shakri, “To ïaïeng riang.” Te ki la ïeng riang pyrshah ïa kata ka shnong.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ha khmih, uwei u nongïathuhlypa u la wan ha u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, bad u la ong, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Me la ïohi ïa une u paidbah babun baroh? ha khmih, ngan ai noh ïa u ha ka kti jong me ha kane ka sngi; bad men sa tip ba ma nga, nga long U Trai.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Ahab u la ong, “Dano?” U te u la ong, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Da ki shakri ki rangbah ki ilaka.’ ” Te u la ong, “Mano ban sdang ïa ka thma?” U la ïathuh te, “Ma me keiñ.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ïalum lang ïa ki shakri ki rangbah ki ilaka, kiba la don arspah laiphew ar ngut: bad hadien jong ki, u la ïalum ïa u paidbah baroh, ïa ki khun Israel baroh keiñ, kiba la don hynñiew hajar ngut.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la ïamih hamar shiteng sngi. Hynrei, u Benhadad u dang dih buaid ha ki ïingjaiñ, ma u bad kita ki syiem, kita ki laiphew ar syiem keiñ kiba ïarap ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kita ki shakri ki rangbah ki ilaka ki la mih noh shuwa; te u Benhadad u la phah khmih, bad ki la ïathuh ïa u, ki ïa-ong, “Don ki briew kiba la mih noh na Samaria.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u la ong, “Lada ki la wan mih ban ïasuk, to kem im ïa ki; lane lada ki wan mih ban ïaleh thma, kem im ïa ki.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, kine ki la mih noh na ka shnong, kita ki shakri samla jong ki rangbah ki ilaka, bad uta u paidïapom uba bud ïa ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki la pynïap uwei uwei ïa la u briew u briew; bad ki Syria ki la phet ïap noh, bad ki Israel ki la beh ïa ki: bad u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria u la phet da u kulai, lem bad ki nongshong kulai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la mih noh, bad u la pom ïa ki kulai bad ïa ki kali, bad u la pynïap ïa ki Syria da ka jingpynïap ba jur.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te uta u nongïathuhlypa u la wan ha u syiem ki Israel, bad u la ong ha u, “Khie leit, pynskhem ïa lade, bad to pyrkhat, to khmih ruh kaei ba men leh: naba ha kata kawei ka snem u syiem ka Syria un wan mih pyrshah ïa me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki shakri u syiem ka Syria ki la ong ha u, “U blei jong ki u long u blei ki lum; namar kata keiñ, ki la kham khlaiñ ban ïa ngi: hynrei, to ngin ïaleh thma ïa ki ha ka madan, bad da shisha ngin kham khlaiñ ban ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad to leh ïa kane; pynkynriah noh ïa kita ki syiem, man u briew na la ka jaka, bad thung da ki kaptan ha ka jaka jong ki:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad to ñiew ïa me u paidïapom, kum uta uba me la duh, ki kulai kajuh, bad ki kali ruh kajuh: bad ngin ïaleh thma ïa ki ha ka madan, bad da shisha ngin kham khlaiñ ban ïa ki.” Bad u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ki, bad u la leh kumta.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ha kata kawei ka snem u Benhadad u la ïalum lang ïa ki Syria, bad u la leit kiew sha Aphek, ban ïaleh ïa ki Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ïa ki khun Israel ruh la ïalum lang, bad la taïar jingbam ïa ki, bad ki la mih ban ïaleh ïa ki: ki khun Israel te ki la shong dara ha khmat jong ki kum ar tylli ki kynhun barit ki khun blang; hynrei, ki Syria ki la pyndap ïa ka ri.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad uta u briew U Blei u la wan bad u la kren ha u syiem ki Israel, bad u la ong, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Namar ba ki nong Syria ki la ong, “Uta U Trai u long u Blei ki lum, hynrei, um long u Blei ki them;” namar kata, ngan ai noh ïa une u paidbah baroh ha ka kti jong me, bad phin sa tip ba ma nga, nga long U Trai.’ ”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki la ïashong dara marpyrshah ïa lade hynñiew sngi. Te ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew ka la long ka jingïaleh; bad ki khun Israel ki la pynïap ha kawei ka sngi na ki Syria shispah hajar ngut kiba ïaleh na tbian.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, kita kiwei ki la phet ïap sha Aphek, shapoh ka shnong; bad ka kynroh ka la twa halor arphew hynñiew hajar ngut kiba dang sah. U Benhadad te u la phet ïap, bad u la wan sha shnong, sha ka kamra kaba kham shapoh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki shakri jong u te ki la ong ha u, “Te ha khmih, ngi la ïohsngew ba ki syiem ka ïing Israel ki long ki syiem kiba isynei: ngi kyrpad ïa me, to ngin buh jaiñ khain ha ki syngkai jong ngi bad ki tyllai ha ki khlieh jong ngi, bad ngin ïaleit mih sha u syiem ki Israel: lehse un pyllait im ïa me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta, ki la panpoh ki jaiñ khain ha la ki syngkai, bad ki la teh tyllai ha la ki khlieh, te haba ki la wan ha u syiem ki Israel, ki la ong, “U Benhadad u shakri jong me u ong, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan im.’ ” U te u la ong, “U dang im? u long u para jong nga.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la khmih thuh dngong, bad ki la pynkloi ban ïoh tip la kata ka long ka jingmut jong u; bad ki la ïa-ong, “U para jong me u Benhadad.” Ynda kumta, u la ong, “To khie leit, wallam ïa u.” Kumta u Benhadad u la wan sha u; bad u la khot ïa u ban wan kiew sha ka kali.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Benhadad u la ong ha u, “Ïa kita ki shnong kiba u kpa jong nga u la knieh na u kpa jong me ngan ai pat; bad men thaw lynti shnong ïa lade ha Damaskos, kumba u kpa jong nga u la thaw ha Samaria.” “Ma nga te,” ong u Ahab, “ngan pyllait ïa me da kane ka jingïakut.” Kumta, ynda u la thaw jutang bad u, u la pyllait ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te uwei u briew na ki khun ki nongïathuhlypa u la ong ha la u lok da ka ktien U Trai, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shoh ïa nga.” Uta u briew te um treh ban shoh ïa u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Namar ba mem shym la kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai, ha khmih, men tang shu khlad bad nga, u sing un pynïap ïa me.” U te, u tang shu ïakhlad bad u, u sing u la shem ïa u, bad u la pynïap ïa u.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, haba u la ïashem ïa uwei pat u briew, u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shoh ïa nga.” Bad uta u briew u la shoh ïa u, da kaba shoh pynmong ïa u.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kumta, uta u nongïathuhlypa u la leit noh, bad u la ap ïa u syiem ha lynti, bad u la riam pynpher ïa lade da kaba spong tap ïa la ki khmat.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad katba u syiem u ïaid nangta, u la pyrta ha u syiem: bad u la ong, “U shakri jong me u la leit hapdeng ka thma; te ha khmih, uwei u briew u la kiar kyrpang, bad u la wallam ïa uwei u briew ha nga, bad u la ong, ‘To sumar ïa une u briew: te lada kumno kumno un jah, ka jingim jong me kan long na ka bynta ka jingim jong u, te lada kumwei, men buria shi talent ka rupa.’",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te katba u shakri jong me u dang donkam shane bad shatai, u la jah noh. U syiem ki Israel te u la ong ha u, ‘Kumta kan long ka jingbishar jong me; me hi me la rai ïa ka.’ ”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad u la pynkloi, bad u la weng noh ïa kata ka jingspong na ki khmat jong u; bad u syiem ki Israel u la ithuh ïa u ba u long na ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Namar me la pyllait na ka kti jong me ïa uba nga la buh ban ïap, namar kata, ka jingim jong me kan long na ka bynta ka jingim jong u, bad ki briew jong me na ka bynta ki briew jong u.’ ”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la leit khuslai bad sngewsih sha la ïing, bad u la wan sha Samaria."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka la jia hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, ba u Naboth u nong Jesril u la don ka brisoh Waiñ, kaba ha Jesril, hajan ka ïingsyiem u Ahab u syiem ka Samaria.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Ahab u la kren ha u Naboth, u da ong, “To ai ha nga ïa ka brisoh Waiñ jong me, ba ngan ïoh pynlong ka kper jhur ïa ka, namar ka long hajan ka ïing jong nga; bad ngan ai pli ïa me da ka brisoh Waiñ kaba kham bha ban ïa ka: lane, lada me sngewdei, ngan ai ïa me ka dor jong ka da ki tyngka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Naboth te u la ong ha u Ahab, “Ka long kaba eh ïa nga ban ai ïa ka ri kynti ki kpa jong nga ha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Ahab u la wan khuslai bad sngewsih sha la ïing namar kata ka ktien kaba u Naboth u nong Jesril u la kren ha u: naba u la ong, “Ngan ym ai ha me ïa ka ri kynti ki kpa jong nga.” Bad u la thiah ha la ka jingthiah, bad u la pynphai noh ïa la ka khmat, bad um treh bam jingbam shuh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba ka Jesebel ka tnga jong u ka la wan ha u, ka la ong ha u, “Balei ba ka mynsiem jong me ka sngewsih katta katta, ba mem bam jingbam shuh?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U te u la ong ha ka, “Namar ba nga la kren ha u Naboth u nong Jesril, bad nga ong ha u, ‘To ai ïa nga ïa ka brisoh Waiñ jong me da ka dor; lane lymda kumta, lada me sngewdei, ngan ai pli ïa me da kawei pat ka brisoh Waiñ’: u la ïathuh te, ‘Ngan ym ai ïa me ïa ka brisoh Waiñ jong nga.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka Jesebel ka tnga jong u ka la ong ha u, “Mem synshar ma me mynta ïa ka hima ki Israel? to khie, bad to bam jingbam, bad pynsngewbha ïa la ka dohnud: ngan ai ïa me ïa ka brisoh Waiñ u Naboth u nong Jesril.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ka la thoh shithi ha ka kyrteng u Ahab, bad ka la pyndait laha ïa ki da ka muhor jong u, bad ka la phah ïa kita ki shithi ha ki rangbah bad ha ki myntri kiba ha ka shnong jong u, kiba la shong bad u Naboth.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka la thoh ha kita ki shithi, ka da ong, “Pynbna ïa ka jingshah jingit, bad to buh ïa u Naboth ha kaba kham jrong hapdeng u paidbah:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad buh ar ngut ki briew, ki khun u Belial, ha khmat jong u, bad to kin sakhi pyrshah ïa u, da kaba ong, ‘Me la tim ïa U Blei bad ïa u syiem.’ Bad hadien kata sa sei ïa u, bad phin lynthem maw ïa u, ba un ïap.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki briew ka shnong jong u, ki rangbah keiñ bad ki myntri kiba shong ha ka shnong jong u, ki la leh kumba ka Jesebel ka la phah sha ki, kat kumba la thoh ha kita ki shithi kiba ka la phah sha ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki la pynbna ka jingshah jingit, bad ki la buh ïa u Naboth ha kaba kham jrong hapdeng u paidbah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kita ar ngut ki briew, ki khun u Belial, ki la rung bad ki la shong ha khmat jong u: bad kita ki briew u Belial ki la sakhi pyrshah ïa u, ïa u Naboth keiñ, ha khmat uta u paidbah, ki da ong, “U Naboth u la tim ïa U Blei bad ïa u syiem.” Ynda kumta, ki la leit lam noh ïa u shabar ka shnong bad ki la lynthem ïa u da ki maw, ha ban da ïap.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la phah sha ka Jesebel, ki ïa-ong, “Ïa u Naboth la lynthem maw, bad u la ïap.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda ka Jesebel ka la ïohsngew ba la lynthem maw ïa u Naboth, bad ba u la ïap, ka Jesebel ka la ong ha u Ahab, “To ïeng, to shim te ïa ka brisoh u Naboth u nong Jesril, kaba um treh ai ïa me da ka dor; naba u Naboth um im shuh, hynrei, u la ïap.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ynda u Ahab u la ïohsngew ba u Naboth u la ïap, u Ahab u la khie joit ban leit hiar sha ka brisoh u Naboth u nong Jesril, ban shimti ïa ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Elijah u nong Tishbi, kaba ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “To ïeng, khie leit ïashem bad u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, uba shong ha Samaria: ha khmih, u don ha ka brisoh u Naboth, sha kaba u la leit hiar ban shimti ïa ka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad men kren ha u da kaba ong, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, “Sha, me la pynïap, me la shimti ruh?” ’ Men kren ruh ha u, da kaba ong, ‘Kumne ong U Trai, “Ha ka jaka ha kaba ki ksew ki la jliah ïa ka snam u Naboth, ki ksew kin jliah ïa ka snam jong me, ka jong me hi keiñ.” ’ ”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Ahab te u la ong ha u Elijah, “Me la shem ïa nga, ko nongshun jong nga?” U te u la ïathuh, “Nga la shem ïa me keiñ: namar me la die noh ïa lade ban leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ‘Ha khmih, ngan wallam ka basniew halor jong me, bad ngan sar noh ïa me baroh phar, bad ngan pynduh noh khoit na u Ahab ïa u khun shynrang baroh, ïa uta uba la set hapoh bad ïa uta uba laitluid ha Israel:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ngan pynlong ïa ka ïing jong me, kum ka ïing u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, bad kum ka ïing u Baasha u khun u Ahijah, namar ka jingpankwah da kaba me la pankwah ïa nga ban bitar, bad me la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad shaphang ka Jesebel ruh U Trai u la kren, u da ong, ‘Ki ksew kin bam ïa ka Jesebel hajan ka kynton Jesril.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ïa uta uba ïap na ki jong u Ahab ha shnong, ki ksew kin bam; bad ïa uta uba ïap ha lum, ki sim bneng kin bam.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> (Hynrei, ym shym don uno uno uba kum u Ahab, uba la die ïa lade ban leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, ïa uba ka Jesebel ka tnga jong u ka la pynkhih.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u la leh da kaba ijli eh ha kaba bud ïa ki bleithaw, kat kum kita baroh ba ki Amor ki la leh, ïa kiba U Trai u la beh ha khmat ki khun Israel.)",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ynda u Ahab u la ïohsngew ïa kita ki ktien, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la kup jaiñ khain ha ka doh jong u, u la shah jingit ruh, bad u la thiah ha ka jaiñ khain, bad u la ïaid jar jar.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka ktien U Trai te ka la wan ha u Elijah u nong Tishbi, ka da ong,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Me ïohi kumno u Ahab u pynrit ïa lade ha khmat jong nga? namar ba u pynrit ïa lade ha khmat jong nga, ngan ym wallam ïa kata ka basniew ha ki sngi jong u: hynrei, ha ki sngi u khun jong u ngan wallam ïa kata ka basniew halor ka ïing jong u.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki la long lai snem khlem jingïaleh thma hapdeng ki Syria bad ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ha ka snem ka balai, u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah u la wan hiar sha u syiem ki Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U syiem ki Israel te u la ong ha ki shakri jong u, “Phim tip ba ka Ramoth-gilead ka long ka jong ngi, bad ngi shu sngap, khlem da knieh ïa ka na ka kti u syiem ka Syria?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Men leit lem bad nga sha ka thma ha Ramoth-gilead?” Bad u Jehoshaphat u la ong ha u syiem ki Israel, “Nga long kumba me long, ki briew jong nga kum ki briew jong me, bad ki kulai jong nga kum ki kulai jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la ong ha u syiem ki Israel, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to kylli ha ka ktien U Trai ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ki Israel u la ïalum lang ïa ki nongïathuhlypa, kumba sawspah ngut, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ngan leit ïaleh ïa ka Ramoth-gilead, ne ngan pep?” Ki te ki la ong, “To leit kiew; naba U Trai un ai noh ïa ka ha ka kti u syiem.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Nalor kine ym don hangne u nongïathuhlypa U Trai, ba ngin ïoh ïakylli na u?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Dang don sa uwei u briew da uba ngi lah ban ïakylli na U Trai, u Mikaïah u khun u Imlah: hynrei, nga isih ïa u; namar um ju ïathuhlypa ka babha shaphang jong nga, hynrei, tang ka basniew.” Te u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Wat ai ba u syiem un ong kumta.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la khot ïa u shakri, bad u la ong, “Wallam kloi ïa u Mikaïah u khun u Imlah.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel bad u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, ki ïashong mar ha ka khet, kiba la phong la ki jaiñ, ha ka madan ha khmat ka khyrdop ka Samaria; bad ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ki la ïathuhlypa ha khmat jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Sedekaïah u khun u Khenaanah u la thaw ïa lade ki reng nar, bad u la ong, “Kumne ong U Trai, ‘Da kine ki reng men tur ïa ki Syria, ha ban da kin duh khoit.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ki la ïathuhlypa kumta, ki ïa-ong, “To leit sha Ramoth-gilead, bad to man bha: naba U Trai un ai noh ïa ka ha ka kti u syiem.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te uta u briew uba leit khot ïa u Mikaïah u la kren ha u, u da ong, “Ha khmih mynta, ki ktien ki nongïathuhlypa ki pyni ka babha ha u syiem da kawei ka shyntur: nga kyrpad ïa me, ai ba ka ktien jong me ruh kan long kum ka ktien jong uwei na ki, bad me ruh to kren ïa ka babha.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Mikaïah te u la ong, “Kumba im U Trai, ïa kaba U Trai un ong ha nga, ïa kata ngan kren.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda u la poi ha u syiem, uta u syiem u la ong ha u, “Ko Mikaïah, ngin leit ïaleh ïa ka Ramoth-gilead, ne ngin pep?” U te u la ïathuh ïa u, “To leit kiew bad to man bha; bad U Trai un ai noh ïa ka ha ka kti u syiem.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U syiem te u la ong ha u, “Katno sien ngan pynsmai ïa me ba men ym kren ha nga ei ei ruh, hynrei, tang ka jingshisha ha ka kyrteng U Trai?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga la ïohi ïa ki Israel baroh ba ki la sakma ha ki lum, kum ki langbrot bymdon nongap; te U Trai u la ong, ‘Kine kim don kynrad; to kin leit phai pat uwei uwei sha la ïing ha kaba suk.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Ngam shym la ïathuh ïa me ba un ym ïathuhlypa ka babha shaphang jong nga, hynrei, tang ka basniew?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U te u la ong, “Namar kata, to sngew ïa ka ktien U Trai: nga la ïohi ïa U Trai ba u shong halor ka khet jong u, bad u paidbah bneng baroh u ïeng hajan jong u sha ka kti kamon jong u bad sha kadiang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, ‘Mano u ban shukor ïa u Ahab, ba un dup leit kiew bad kyllon ha Ramoth-gilead?’ Te uwei u la ong da kumne, uwei pat da kumtai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te la wan mih u mynsiem, bad u la ïeng ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ong, ‘Ngan shukor ïa u.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u, ‘Da kumno?’ U te u la ong, ‘Ngan leit mih, bad ngan long u mynsiem balamler ha ka shyntur ki nongïathuhlypa jong u baroh.’ U te u la ong, ‘Men shukor ïa u, bad men lah ruh: to leit mih, bad to leh kumta.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata te, ha khmih, U Trai u la buh ïa u mynsiem balamler ha ka shyntur kine ki nongïathuhlypa jong me baroh; bad U Trai u la kren ïa ka basniew shaphang jong me.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sedekaïah u khun u Khenaanah u la wan hajan, bad u la thab ïa u Mikaïah ha ka ngab, bad u la ong, “Da kano ka lad U Mynsiem U Trai u la mih na nga ban wan kren ha me?”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Mikaïah te u la ong, “Ha khmih, men sa ïohi ha kata ka sngi, ynda men leit rung sha ka kamra kaba kham shapoh ban buhrieh ïa lade?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U syiem ki Israel te u la ong, “Shim ïa u Mikaïah, bad leit lam pat ïa u sha u Amon u nongsynshar ka shnong, bad ha u Joash u khun u syiem;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ong, ‘Kumne u ong u syiem, “Thep phatok ïa une u briew, bad bsa ïa u da u kpu ka jingsaja bad da ka um ka jingsaja, ha ban da ngan wan ha kaba suk.” ’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Mikaïah u la ong, “Lada men dang ïoh wan phai pat ha kaba suk, U Trai um shym kren ha nga.” U la ong ruh, “To sngew, phi ki paidbah, phi baroh keiñ.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumta, u syiem ki Israel bad u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah ki la ïaleit kiew sha Ramoth-gilead.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Ngan riam pher ïa lade, bad ngan tur sha ka jingïaleh; hynrei, ma me, phong la ki jong ki jaiñ.” Kumta u syiem ki Israel u la riam pher ïa lade, bad u la leit tur sha ka jingïaleh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u syiem ka Syria u la lah hukum ïa ki laiphew ar ngut ki kaptan ki kali ïapom jong u, u da ong, “Wat ïaleh bad ki barit lymne ki bakhraw, hynrei, tang bad u syiem ki Israel hi.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ynda ki kaptan ki kali ïapom ki la ïohi ïa u Jehoshaphat, ki la ïa-ong, “Da shisha u dei u syiem ki Israel;” bad ki la phai noh ban ïaleh ïa u: bad u Jehoshaphat u la kyang jam.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ynda ki kaptan ki kali ki la ïohi ba um shym dei u syiem ki Israel; ki la kylla pat na kaba beh ïa u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te uwei u briew u la shu siat pathar, bad u la leit dei ïa u syiem ki Israel hapdeng ki jingpyndait ki sopti ïapom jong u: namar kata u la ong ha u khashwan ka kali jong u, “To pynphai ïa ka kti jong me, bad leit lam noh ïa nga na u paidïapom; naba nga la mynsaw jur.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ka thma ka la nang jur ha kata ka sngi: te ïa u syiem la pynïeng ha ka kali jong u ban ïaleh ïa ki Syria, bad u la ïap ha ka por janmiet: te ka snam ka la tuid na kata ka jingmong ha tbian ka kali.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te la mih ka jingpyrta lyngba u paidïapom hamar kaba sep ka sngi, kaba ong, “To u briew baroh sha la ka shnong, bad u briew baroh sha la ka ri.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kumta, u syiem u la ïap, bad la leit lam sha Samaria; bad ki la tep ïa u syiem ha Samaria.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad ki la sait ïa ka kali harud ka pung Samaria; bad ki ksew ki la ïa-jliah ïa ka snam jong u, (te ki nuti ki ju sum ïa lade hangta;) kat kum ka ktien U Trai kaba u la kren.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Ahab, bad baroh kaba u la leh, bad ka ïing bniat hati kaba u la tei, bad ki shnong baroh kiba u la tei, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ki Israel?",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, u Ahab u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u; bad u Ahasaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Jehoshaphat u khun u Asa u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Judah ha ka snem ka basaw jong u Ahab u syiem ki Israel.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U Jehoshaphat u la long laiphew san snem ka rta mynba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar arphew san snem ha Jerusalem. Bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Asubah” ka khun u Shilhi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti u Asa u kpa jong u baroh; um shym phai noh na ka, u da leh ïa kata kaba dei ha ki khmat U Trai: la kumta ym shym la pynduh noh ïa ki jaka bajrong; u paidbah u dang kñia bad u thang jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la pynlong ka jingïasuk bad u syiem ki Israel.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te kita kiwei ki jingleh u Jehoshaphat, bad ka bor jong u kaba u la pyni, bad kumno u la ïaleh thma, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl Ki Syiem Ka Judah?",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad kiba dang sah na ki kynja Sodom, kiba la dang sah ha ki sngi u kpa jong u, u Asa, u la pynduh noh na ka ri.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te ym shym la don syiem ha Edom: u lyngskor u la long u syiem.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U Jehoshaphat u la thaw ki lieng Tarshish ban leit sha Ophir ban ïoh ka ksiar: hynrei, kim shym ïoh leit; namar ki lieng ki la pait ha Esion-geber.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ynda kumta, u Ahasaïah u khun u Ahab u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “To shah ïa ki shakri jong nga ban leit lem bad ki shakri jong me ha ki lieng.” Hynrei, u Jehoshaphat um treh.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Te u Jehoshaphat u la thiah noh bad ki kpa jong u, bad la tep ïa u lem bad ki kpa jong u ha ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u: bad u Jehoram u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U Ahasaïah u khun u Ahab u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Israel ha Samaria ha ka bakhathynñiew snem u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, bad u la synshar ar snem halor ki Israel.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti u kpa jong u, bad ha ka lynti ka kmie jong u, bad ha ka lynti u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, ha kaba u la pynleh pop ïa ki Israel.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Bad u la leit shakri ïa u Baal ruh, bad u la mane ïa u, bad u la pynbitar ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, katba kum kata baroh ba u kpa jong u, u la leh."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;